"change the :ref:`Add to Cart <ecommerce/checkout/add-to-cart>` button's "
"behavior,"
msgstr ""
"ändra :ref:`Lägg i varukorg <ecommerce/checkout/add-to-cart>`-knappens "
"beteende,"

