":doc:`building blocks <../website/web_design/building_blocks>` eller öppna "
"fliken :guilabel:`Customize` för att aktivera olika kassaoptioner."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:145
msgid "Content added through building blocks is **specific** to each step."
msgstr ""
"Innehåll som lagts till genom byggmoduler är **specifikt** för varje steg."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:148
msgid ""
"Restrict access to the :ref:`shop <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>` "
"and :ref:`checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>` for "
"specific customers, e.g., in a :doc:`B2B <b2b_b2c>` business setup."
msgstr ""
"Omezte přístup k :ref:`obchodu <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>` a "
":ref:`pokladně <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>` pro konkrétní "
"zákazníky, např. v nastavení :doc:`B2B <b2b_b2c>` podnikání."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:155
msgid "Review order"
msgstr "Granska beställning"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:157
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Review Order` step allows customers to see the items they "
"added to their cart, adjust quantities, or :guilabel:`Remove` products. "
"Information related to the product prices and taxes applied are also "
"displayed. Customers can then click the :guilabel:`Checkout` button to "
"continue to the :ref:`Delivery <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>` step."
msgstr ""
"Steget :guilabel:`Review Order` gör det möjligt för kunder att se de "
"artiklar de lagt till i sin kundvagn, justera kvantiteter eller "
":guilabel:`Remove` produkter. Information om produktpriser och tillämpade "
"skatter visas också. Kunder kan sedan klicka på knappen :guilabel:`Checkout` "
"för att fortsätta till steget :ref:`Delivery <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:162
msgid ""
"Open the website editor to :ref:`enable <ecommerce/checkout/"
"customize_steps>` checkout options such as:"
msgstr ""
"Öppna hemsideredigeraren för att :ref:`aktivera <ecommerce/checkout/"
"customize_steps>` utcheckningsalternativ som:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:165
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Suggested Accessories`: to showcase :ref:`accessory products "
"<ecommerce/cross_upselling/accessory>`;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Suggested Accessories`: för att visa upp :ref:`accessory products "
"<ecommerce/cross_upselling/accessory>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:167
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Promo Code`: to allow customers to redeem :ref:`gift cards "
"<ewallet_gift/gift-cards>` or apply :doc:`discount codes <../../sales/sales/"
"products_prices/loyalty_discount>`;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Promo Code`: för att tillåta kunder att lösa in :ref:`gift cards "
"<ewallet_gift/gift-cards>` eller tillämpa :doc:`discount codes <../../sales/"
"sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:169
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add to Wishlist`: :ref:`Enable wishlists <ecommerce/products/"
"wishlists>` to allow signed-in users to remove a product from their cart and "
"add it to their wishlist using the :guilabel:`Save for later` option."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lägg till i önskelista`: :ref:`Aktivera önskelistor <ecommerce/"
"products/wishlists>` för att tillåta inloggade användare att ta bort en "
"produkt från kundvagnen och lägga till den i önskelistan med alternativet "
":guilabel:`Spara för senare`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:174
msgid ""
"If a :doc:`fiscal position <../../finance/accounting/taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>` is detected automatically, the product tax is determined "
"based on the customer's IP address."
msgstr ""
"Om en :doc:`skatteposition <../../finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions>"
"` upptäcks automatiskt bestäms produktskatten baserat på kundens IP-adress."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:176
msgid ""
"If the installed :doc:`payment provider <../../finance/payment_providers>` "
"supports :ref:`express checkout <payment_providers/express_checkout>`, a "
"dedicated button is displayed, allowing customers to go straight from the "
"cart to the confirmation page without filling out the contact form."
msgstr ""
"Om den installerade :doc:`betalningsleverantören <../../finance/"
"payment_providers>` stöder :ref:`expressutcheckning <payment_providers/"
"express_checkout>`, visas en dedikerad knapp som gör det möjligt för kunder "
"att gå direkt från varukorgen till bekräftelsesidan utan att fylla i "
"kontaktformuläret."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:184
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:3
msgid "Delivery"
msgstr "Leverans"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:186
msgid "Once they have reviewed their order:"
msgstr "När de har granskat sin beställning:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:188
msgid ""
"Unsigned-in customers are prompted to :guilabel:`Sign in` or enter "
"their :guilabel:`Email address`, along with their delivery address and phone "
"details;"
msgstr ""
"Kunder som inte är inloggade uppmanas att :guilabel:`Sign in` eller ange sin "
":guilabel:`Email address`, tillsammans med sin leveransadress och "
"telefonuppgifter;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:190
msgid ""
"Signed-in customers can select the appropriate :guilabel:`Delivery address`."
msgstr "Inloggade kunder kan välja lämplig :guilabel:`Leveransadress`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:192
msgid ""
"They can then :doc:`choose a delivery method <shipping>`, select or enter "
"their :guilabel:`Billing Address` (or toggle the :guilabel:`Same as delivery "
"address` switch if the billing and delivery addresses are identical), and "
"click :guilabel:`Confirm` to proceed to the next step."
msgstr ""
"De kan sedan :doc:`välja en leveransmetod <shipping>`, välja eller ange sin "
":guilabel:`Faktureringsadress` (eller aktivera växeln :guilabel:`Samma som "
"leveransadress` om fakturerings- och leveransadresserna är identiska) och "
"klicka på :guilabel:`Bekräfta` för att fortsätta till nästa steg."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:197
msgid ""
"For B2B customers, you can also :ref:`enable <ecommerce/checkout/"
"customize_steps>` optional :ref:`B2B fields <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/b2b-fields>` "
"in the website editor."
msgstr ""
"För B2B-kunder kan du också :ref:`aktivera <ecommerce/checkout/"
"customize_steps>` valfria :ref:`B2B-fält <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/b2b-fields>` i "
"hemsideredigeraren."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:199
msgid ""
"You can add a checkbox for users without an account to sign up for a "
"newsletter. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`. Under the :guilabel:`Shop - Checkout Process` section, enable "
"the :guilabel:`Newsletter` feature and select a :guilabel:`Newsletter List`."
msgstr ""
"Du kan lägga till en kryssruta för användare utan konto att anmäla sig till "
"ett nyhetsbrev. För att göra detta, gå till :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. Under sektionen :guilabel:`Shop - Checkout "
"Process`, aktivera funktionen :guilabel:`Newsletter` och välj en "
":guilabel:`Newsletter List`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:207
msgid "Extra info"
msgstr "Extra information"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:209
msgid ""
"You can add an :guilabel:`Extra Info` step in the checkout process to "
"collect additional customer information through an online form, which is "
"then included in the :ref:`sales order <handling/sales>`. To do "
"so, :ref:`enable <ecommerce/checkout/customize_steps>` the :guilabel:`Extra "
"Step` option in the website editor. The form can be :ref:`customized "
"<website/building_blocks/form>` as needed."
msgstr ""
"Du kan lägga till ett :guilabel:`Extra Info`-steg i kassaprocessen för att "
"samla in ytterligare kundinformation via ett onlineformulär, som sedan "
"inkluderas i :ref:`sales order <handling/sales>`. För att göra detta, "
":ref:`enable <ecommerce/checkout/customize_steps>` alternativet "
":guilabel:`Extra Step` i hemsideredigeraren. Formuläret kan :ref:`customized "
"<website/building_blocks/form>` efter behov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:216
msgid ""
"Alternatively, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, scroll to the :guilabel:`Shop - Checkout Process` section, "
"enable :guilabel:`Extra Step During Checkout`, and click :guilabel:`Save`. "
"Click :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Configure Form` to customize it."
msgstr ""
"Alternativt, gå till :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, skrolla till sektionen :guilabel:`Shop - Checkout Process`, "
"aktivera :guilabel:`Extra Step During Checkout` och klicka på "
":guilabel:`Save`. Klicka på :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Configure "
"Form` för att anpassa det."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:223
msgid "Payment"
msgstr "Betalning"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:225
msgid ""
"At the :guilabel:`Payment` step, customers :guilabel:`Choose a payment "
"method`, enter their payment details, and click :guilabel:`Pay now`."
msgstr ""
"I steget :guilabel:`Payment` :guilabel:`Choose a payment method`, anger sina "
"betalningsuppgifter och klickar på :guilabel:`Pay now`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:228
msgid ""
"You can require customers to agree to your :doc:`terms and conditions <../../"
"finance/accounting/customer_invoices/terms_conditions>` before payment. "
"To :ref:`enable <ecommerce/checkout/customize_steps>` this option, go to the "
"website editor and toggle the :guilabel:`Accept Terms & Conditions` feature."
msgstr ""
"Du kan kräva att kunder godkänner dina :doc:`terms and conditions <../../"
"finance/accounting/customer_invoices/terms_conditions>` före betalning. För "
"att :ref:`enable <ecommerce/checkout/customize_steps>` detta alternativ, gå "
"till hemsideredigeraren och aktivera funktionen :guilabel:`Accept Terms & "
"Conditions`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:234
msgid ""
"Enable the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` and click the :icon:`fa-"
"bug` (:guilabel:`bug`) icon to display an :ref:`availability "
"<payment_providers/availability>` report for payment providers and payment "
"methods, which helps diagnose potential availability issues on the payment "
"form."
msgstr ""
"Aktivera :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` och klicka på ikonen "
":icon:`fa-bug` (:guilabel:`bug`) för att visa en :ref:`availability "
"<payment_providers/availability>`-rapport för betalningsleverantörer och "
"betalningsmetoder, vilket hjälper till att diagnostisera potentiella "
"tillgänglighetsproblem på betalningsformuläret."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:242
msgid "Order confirmation"
msgstr "Orderbekräftelse"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:244
msgid ""
"The final step of the checkout process is the :guilabel:`Order "
"confirmation`, which provides a summary of the customer's purchase details."
msgstr ""
"Det sista steget i kassaprocessen är :guilabel:`Order confirmation`, som ger "
"en sammanfattning av kundens köpdetaljer."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:248
msgid ":doc:`Order handling documentation <order_handling>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Dokumentation om orderhantering <order_handling>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:3
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:124
msgid "Customer accounts"
msgstr "Kundkonton"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:5
msgid ""
"Using customer accounts for an ecommerce shop enables you to :ref:`manage "
"customers <ecommerce/customer_accounts/account-creation>`, control access to "
"the :ref:`shop <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>`, "
"the :ref:`checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>`, or "
"the :ref:`customer portal <portal/access>`, and support both :doc:`B2B and "
"B2C operations <b2b_b2c>`."
msgstr ""
"Použití zákaznických účtů pro webový obchod vám umožňuje :ref:`spravovat "
"zákazníky <ecommerce/customer_accounts/account-creation>`, kontrolovat "
"přístup k :ref:`obchodu <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>`, "
":ref:`pokladně <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>` nebo "
":ref:`zákaznickému portálu <portal/access>` a podporovat :doc:`operace B2B i "
"B2C <b2b_b2c>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:11
msgid ""
"After logging in, customers can access their :doc:`customer portal <../../"
"general/users/portal>` by clicking their username in the top-right corner of "
"the screen and selecting :guilabel:`My Account`. From there, they can view "
"all their documents in one place, such as quotations, orders, invoices, and "
"more."
msgstr ""
"Po přihlášení mohou zákazníci přistupovat ke svému :doc:`zákaznickému "
"portálu <../../general/users/portal>` kliknutím na své uživatelské jméno v "
"pravém horním rohu obrazovky a výběrem :guilabel:`My Account`. Odtud mohou "
"zobrazit všechny své dokumenty na jednom místě, jako jsou nabídky, "
"objednávky, faktury a další."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:None
msgid "Customer account access"
msgstr "Åtkomst till kundkonto"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:20
msgid ""
"The customer account page can be customized with building blocks and other "
"features through the :doc:`website builder <../website/web_design>`."
msgstr ""
"Stránku zákaznického účtu lze přizpůsobit pomocí stavebních bloků a dalších "
"funkcí prostřednictvím :doc:`nástroje pro tvorbu webu <../website/web_design>"
"`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:26
msgid "Customer account creation"
msgstr "Skapande av kundkonto"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:28
msgid ""
"You can choose whether customer accounts and document access are available "
"to everyone or restricted to invited users only. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, then scroll down "
"to the :guilabel:`Privacy` section. Under :guilabel:`Customer Account`, "
"select one of the following options:"
msgstr ""
"Můžete si vybrat, zda jsou zákaznické účty a přístup k dokumentům dostupné "
"všem, nebo omezeny pouze na pozvané uživatele. Přejděte na "
":menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, poté přejděte dolů "
"do sekce :guilabel:`Privacy`. Pod :guilabel:`Customer Account` vyberte jednu "
"z následujících možností:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:33
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On invitation`: Customers can only create an account if the "
"website owner sends them an invitation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`På inbjudan`: Kunder kan bara skapa ett konto om hemsidans ägare "
"skickar dem en inbjudan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:35
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Free sign up`: Every website visitor can create an account and "
"sign in. They will get access to the :doc:`portal <../../general/users/"
"portal>` by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Free sign up`: Každý návštěvník webu si může vytvořit účet a "
"přihlásit se. Automaticky získají přístup na :doc:`portál <../../general/"
"users/portal>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:40
msgid "To send an email invitation to a customer:"
msgstr "Så här skickar du en e-postinbjudan till en kund:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:42
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Customers`."
msgstr "Gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> Webbshop --> Kunder`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:43
msgid ""
"Select a customer or click :guilabel:`New` to create one, ensuring "
"an :guilabel:`Email` address is set."
msgstr ""
"Välj en kund eller klicka på :guilabel:`Skapa` för att skapa en, och "
"säkerställ att en :guilabel:`E-post`-adress är angiven."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:45
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(Actions)` icon next to the record's "
"name at the top-left and select :guilabel:`Grant portal access`."
msgstr ""
"Klicka på ikonen :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(Åtgärder)` bredvid postens namn "
"längst upp till vänster och välj :guilabel:`Bevilja portaltillgång`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:47
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Portal Access Management` pop-up, click :guilabel:`Grant "
"Access` to send the invitation."
msgstr ""
"I popup-fönstret :guilabel:`Hantering av portaltillgång` klickar du på "
":guilabel:`Bevilja tillgång` för att skicka inbjudan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:51
msgid ""
"To invite multiple customers at once, switch to the customers :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`List` view, select several customers, click the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Actions` button, and select :guilabel:`Grant portal access`."
msgstr ""
"För att bjuda in flera kunder samtidigt, växla till kundernas :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`List`-vy, välj flera kunder, klicka på knappen :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Åtgärder` och välj :guilabel:`Bevilja portaltillgång`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:55
msgid ""
"Once done, the customer(s) receive an email confirming their account "
"creation, including instructions on setting a password and activating their "
"account."
msgstr ""
"När det är klart får kunden/kunderna ett e-postmeddelande som bekräftar att "
"deras konto har skapats, inklusive instruktioner om hur man ställer in ett "
"lösenord och aktiverar sitt konto."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:59
msgid ""
"When selecting the :guilabel:`Free sign up`, a clickable :guilabel:`Don't "
"have an account?` link appears under the login form on the website."
msgstr ""
"När du väljer :guilabel:`Fri registrering` visas en klickbar :guilabel:`Har "
"du inget konto?`-länk under inloggningsformuläret på hemsidan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:61
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`On invitation` option is especially useful for :ref:`B2B "
"<ecommerce/b2b_b2c/prices>` businesses that prefer to keep :ref:`prices "
"hidden <ecommerce/prices/hide-prices>` on the website and grant access only "
"to invited customers."
msgstr ""
"Alternativet :guilabel:`På inbjudan` är särskilt användbart för :ref:`B2B "
"<ecommerce/b2b_b2c/prices>`-företag som föredrar att hålla :ref:`priser "
"dolda <ecommerce/prices/hide-prices>` på hemsidan och bevilja tillgång "
"endast till inbjudna kunder."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:66
msgid ""
"It is possible to configure a website form with a :guilabel:`Create a "
"Customer` :ref:`action <website/building_blocks/action>` to automatically "
"create a customer record in the backend when filled in."
msgstr ""
"Det är möjligt att konfigurera ett hemsideformulär med en :guilabel:`Skapa "
"en kund` :ref:`åtgärd <website/building_blocks/action>` för att automatiskt "
"skapa en kundpost i backend när det fylls i."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:71
msgid "Access restriction"
msgstr "Begränsning av åtkomst"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:73
msgid ""
"Once a customer account is created, it is still possible to adjust the "
"access rights either globally or for individual users:"
msgstr ""
"När ett kundkonto har skapats är det fortfarande möjligt att justera "
"åtkomstbehörigheterna antingen globalt eller för enskilda användare:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:76
msgid ""
":ref:`Revoke access or re-invite a customer <portal/access>` using the "
"related buttons in the :guilabel:`Portal Access Management` pop-up."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Odvolejte přístup nebo znovu pozvěte zákazníka <portal/access>` pomocí "
"příslušných tlačítek v okně :guilabel:`Portal Access Management`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:78
msgid ""
"Restrict :ref:`access to the shop <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>`;"
msgstr ""
"Begränsa :ref:`tillgång till butiken <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-"
"access>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:79
msgid ""
"Decide whether customers need to create an account to :ref:`complete the "
"checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>`."
msgstr ""
"Besluta om kunder behöver skapa ett konto för att :ref:`slutföra kassan "
"<ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:83
msgid ""
"It is also possible to define the types of documents customers have access "
"to. To do so, click your username in the upper-right corner of the website, "
"select :guilabel:`My Account` and open the :doc:`website builder <../website/"
"web_design>`. On the :guilabel:`Customize` tab, enable or disable access to "
"specific documents as needed."
msgstr ""
"Det är också möjligt att definiera vilka typer av dokument kunder har "
"tillgång till. För att göra detta, klicka på ditt användarnamn i det övre "
"högra hörnet av hemsidan, välj :guilabel:`Mitt konto` och öppna "
":doc:`hemsidesverktyget <../website/web_design>`. På fliken "
":guilabel:`Anpassa`, aktivera eller avaktivera tillgång till specifika "
"dokument efter behov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:91
msgid "Shop access"
msgstr "Butikstillgång"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:93
msgid ""
"To restrict access to the entire online shop for users who are not logged-"
"in, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll "
"to :guilabel:`Privacy` and under :guilabel:`Ecommerce Access`, "
"select :guilabel:`Logged in users`. Select :guilabel:`All users` if the shop "
"should be visible to every website visitor."
msgstr ""
"För att begränsa tillgången till hela webbshopen för användare som inte är "
"inloggade, gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> Konfiguration --> "
"Inställningar`, scrolla till :guilabel:`Integritet` och under "
":guilabel:`Tillgång till webbshop`, välj :guilabel:`Inloggade användare`. "
"Välj :guilabel:`Alla användare` om butiken ska vara synlig för alla besökare "
"på hemsidan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:99
msgid ""
"To restrict access to the shop's pricing, use :ref:`pricelists <ecommerce/"
"prices/pricelists>` with :ref:`country groups <ecommerce/prices/country-"
"groups>`."
msgstr ""
"För att begränsa tillgången till butikens priser, använd :ref:`prislistor "
"<ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` med :ref:`landsgrupper <ecommerce/prices/"
"country-groups>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:105
msgid "Checkout access"
msgstr "Kassakåtkomst"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:107
msgid ""
"To allow customers to checkout as guests or force them to sign in/create an "
"account, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, "
"scroll down to the :guilabel:`Shop - Checkout Process` section, and "
"configure the :guilabel:`Sign in/up at checkout` setting. The following "
"options are available:"
msgstr ""
"För att tillåta kunder att checka ut som gäster eller tvinga dem att logga "
"in/skapa ett konto, gå till :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, skrolla ner till sektionen :guilabel:`Shop - Checkout Process` "
"och konfigurera inställningen :guilabel:`Sign in/up at checkout`. Följande "
"optioner är tillgängliga:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:112
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Optional`: Customers can check out as guests and register later "
"via the order confirmation email to track their order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Valfritt`: Kunder kan checka ut som gäster och registrera sig "
"senare via orderbekräftelsemejlet för att följa sin beställning."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:114
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Disabled (buy as guest)`: Customers can checkout as guests "
"without creating an account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Disabled (buy as guest)`: Kunder kan checka ut som gäster utan "
"att skapa ett konto."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:115
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Mandatory (no guest checkout)`: Customers must sign in or create "
"an account at the :ref:`Review Order <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>` step "
"to complete their purchase."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Mandatory (no guest checkout)`: Kunder måste logga in eller skapa "
"ett konto i steget :ref:`Review Order <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>` för "
"att slutföra sitt köp."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:119
msgid ""
"Settings are specific to each website, allowing you to configure a B2C "
"website with guest checkout and a B2B website that requires customers to "
"sign in."
msgstr ""
"Inställningarna är specifika för varje hemsida, vilket gör att du kan "
"konfigurera en B2C-hemsida med gästkassa och en B2B-hemsida som kräver att "
"kunder loggar in."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:121
msgid ""
"To use the :ref:`wishlist <ecommerce/products/wishlists>` feature, customers "
"must create an account to save their favorite items for later."
msgstr ""
"För att använda funktionen :ref:`önskelista <ecommerce/products/wishlists>` "
"måste kunder skapa ett konto för att spara sina favoritobjekt för senare."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:127
msgid "Multi-website account"
msgstr "Konto för flera webbplatser"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:129
msgid ""
"When managing multiple websites, it is possible to make customer accounts "
"available across *all* websites, allowing each customer to use a single "
"account. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, in the :guilabel:`Privacy` section, enable the :guilabel:`Shared "
"Customer Accounts` option."
msgstr ""
"När du hanterar flera hemsidor är det möjligt att göra kundkonton "
"tillgängliga över *alla* hemsidor, vilket gör det möjligt för varje kund att "
"använda ett enda konto. För att göra detta, gå till "
":menuselection:`Hemsida --> Konfiguration --> Inställningar`, i sektionen "
":guilabel:`Integritet`, aktivera alternativet :guilabel:`Delade kundkonton`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/customer_accounts.rst:135
msgid ""
"When operating both :ref:`B2B and B2C online shops <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/"
"multiple-websites>`, it is recommended to use separate websites for each "
"business model."
msgstr ""
"När du driver både :ref:`B2B- och B2C-webbshoppar <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/"
"multiple-websites>` rekommenderas det att använda separata hemsidor för "
"varje affärsmodell."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:3
msgid "Order handling"
msgstr "Hantering av order"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:5
msgid ""
"When a customer orders on your eCommerce, there are **three** record types "
"required to be handle in Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"När en kund beställer i din e-handel finns det **tre** posttyper som måste "
"hanteras i Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:8
msgid ":ref:`Sales orders <handling/sales>`;"
msgstr ":ref:`Försäljningsorder <hantering/försäljning>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:9
msgid ":ref:`Delivery orders <handling/delivery>`;"
msgstr ":ref:`Delivery orders <hantering/delivery>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:10
msgid ":ref:`Invoices & legal requirements <handling/legal>`."
msgstr ":ref:`Fakturor & juridiska krav <hantering/legal>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:15
msgid "Sales orders"
msgstr "Försäljningsorder"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:18
msgid "Order and payment status"
msgstr "Order- och betalningsstatus"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:20
msgid ""
"The first step when a customer adds a product to his cart is the creation of "
"a quotation. Orders can be managed either from the **Website** "
"or :doc:`Sales </applications/sales/sales>` app. eCommerce orders can "
"automatically be assigned to a specific sales team by going "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`. In the **Shop - "
"Checkout Process** section, select a :guilabel:`Sales Team` "
"or :guilabel:`Salesperson` to handle eCommerce orders."
msgstr ""
"Det första steget när en kund lägger en produkt i sin kundvagn är att skapa "
"en offert. Beställningar kan hanteras antingen från appen **Webbplats** "
"eller :doc:`Sales </applications/sales/sales>`. e-handelsbeställningar kan "
"automatiskt tilldelas ett specifikt säljteam genom att gå "
"till :menuselection:`Webbplats --> Konfiguration --> Inställningar`. I "
"avsnittet **Shop - Checkout Process** väljer du ett :guilabel:`Sales Team` "
"eller :guilabel:`Salesperson` som ska hantera e-handelsbeställningar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:None
msgid "Assignment of online orders to a sales team or salesperson"
msgstr "Tilldelning av onlinebeställningar till ett säljteam eller en säljare"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:30
msgid ""
"Orders can be found under :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Orders/"
"Unpaid Orders`. Each order goes through a different status:"
msgstr ""
"Beställningar hittar du under :menuselection:`Webbplats --> e-handel --> "
"Beställningar/ Obetalda beställningar`. Varje order genomgår olika status:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:33
msgid ""
"**Quotation**: a new product is added to the cart, but the customer has "
"*not* gone through the checkout process yet;"
msgstr ""
"**Citat**: En ny produkt läggs i varukorgen, men kunden har *inte* gått "
"igenom kassaprocessen ännu;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:35
msgid ""
"**Quotation sent**: the customer has gone through the checkout process and "
"confirmed the order, but the payment is not yet confirmed;"
msgstr ""
"**Quotation sent**: kunden har gått igenom kassaprocessen och bekräftat "
"beställningen, men betalningen är ännu inte bekräftad;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:37
msgid ""
"**Order**: the customer has gone through the checkout process, confirmed the "
"order, and the payment is received."
msgstr ""
"**Order**: kunden har gått igenom kassaprocessen, bekräftat ordern och "
"betalningen är mottagen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:None
msgid "Statuses of eCommerce orders"
msgstr "Status för e-handelsorder"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:45
msgid "Abandoned cart"
msgstr "Övergiven vagn"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:47
msgid ""
"An **abandoned cart** represents an order for which the customer did **not "
"finish** the checkout confirmation process. For these orders, it is possible "
"to send an **email reminder** to the customer automatically. To enable that "
"feature, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings` and "
"in the :guilabel:`Email & Marketing` section, "
"enable :guilabel:`Automatically send abandoned checkout emails`. Once "
"enabled, you can set the **time-lapse** after which the email is sent and "
"customize the **email template** used."
msgstr ""
"En **övergiven kundvagn** är en order för vilken kunden **inte slutförde** "
"bekräftelseprocessen i kassan. För dessa beställningar är det möjligt att "
"automatiskt skicka en **e-postpåminnelse** till kunden. För att aktivera den "
"funktionen, gå till :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings` "
"och i :guilabel:`Email & Marketing` avsnittet, "
"aktivera :guilabel:`Automatically send abandoned checkout emails`. När det "
"är aktiverat kan du ställa in **tidsfördröjning** efter vilken e-"
"postmeddelandet skickas och anpassa **e-postmallen** som används."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:55
msgid ""
"For abandoned cart emails, the customer must either have entered their "
"contact details during the checkout process; or be logged-in when they added "
"the product to their cart."
msgstr ""
"För e-postmeddelanden om övergivna varukorgar måste kunden antingen ha "
"angett sina kontaktuppgifter under utcheckningsprocessen eller vara inloggad "
"när de lade till produkten i sin varukorg."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:61
msgid "Delivery orders"
msgstr "Leveransbeställningar"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:64
msgid "Delivery flow"
msgstr "Leveransflöde"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:66
msgid ""
"Once a quotation has been confirmed, a delivery order is automatically "
"created. The next step is to process this delivery."
msgstr ""
"När en offert har bekräftats skapas automatiskt en leveransorder. Nästa steg "
"är att behandla denna leverans."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:69
msgid ""
"Packing eCommerce orders usually requires picking the product, preparing the "
"packaging, printing the shipping label(s) and shipping to the customer. "
"Depending on the number of orders, strategy, or resources, those steps can "
"be considered as one or multiple actions in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Att packa e-handelsorder innebär vanligtvis att plocka produkten, förbereda "
"förpackningen, skriva ut fraktsedeln/fraktsedlarna och skicka till kunden. "
"Beroende på antalet beställningar, strategi eller resurser kan dessa steg "
"betraktas som en eller flera åtgärder i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:73
msgid ""
"An automatic email can be sent to the customer when the transfer status in "
"Odoo is “done”. To do so, enable the feature in the settings of "
"the :doc:`Inventory </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory>` app."
msgstr ""
"Ett automatiskt e-postmeddelande kan skickas till kunden när "
"överföringsstatusen i Odoo är \"klar\". För att göra detta, aktivera "
"funktionen i inställningarna för :doc:`Inventory </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory>` app."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:78
msgid ""
"If customers are allowed to pay when picking up their order in stores or by "
"wire transfer, the quotation is **not** be confirmed and the stock is "
"**not** be reserved. Orders must be confirmed manually to reserve products "
"in stock."
msgstr ""
"Om kunderna tillåts betala när de hämtar sin beställning i butik eller via "
"banköverföring, är offerten **inte** bekräftad och lagret **inte** "
"reserverat. Beställningar måste bekräftas manuellt för att reservera "
"produkter i lager."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:83
msgid ""
":doc:`../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/invoicing`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/invoicing`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:84
msgid ""
":doc:`../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/labels`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/labels`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:85
msgid ""
":doc:`../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/multipack`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/multipack`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:88
msgid "Returns and refunds"
msgstr "Returer och återbetalningar"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:90
msgid ""
"Customers can only return an order through an online form. It may not be "
"possible to return products depending on the return strategy or type of "
"product."
msgstr ""
"Kunder kan endast returnera en beställning via ett onlineformulär. Det kan "
"hända att det inte är möjligt att returnera produkter beroende på "
"returstrategi eller typ av produkt."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:93
msgid ""
"Full refunds can be directly sent to customers from within the order "
"interface. A refund-compatible payment provider needs to be enabled first."
msgstr ""
"Fullständiga återbetalningar kan skickas direkt till kunder från "
"ordergränssnittet. En betalningsleverantör som är kompatibel med "
"återbetalningar måste aktiveras först."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:97
msgid ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:98
msgid ":doc:`/applications/services/helpdesk/advanced/after_sales`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applikationer/tjänster/helpdesk/avancerat/after_sales`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:99
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/payment_providers`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/payment_providers`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:104
msgid "Invoice and legal requirements"
msgstr "Fakturering och rättsliga krav"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:106
msgid ""
"The final step of an ecommerce order is to generate the invoice and send it "
"to the customer. Depending on your needs, an invoice can either be generated "
"automatically or on demand of the customer. This process can be automated if "
"(and when) the online payment is :ref:`confirmed <handling/sales>`."
msgstr ""
"Det sista steget i en webbshopsbeställning är att skapa fakturan och skicka "
"den till kunden. Beroende på dina behov kan en faktura antingen skapas "
"automatiskt eller på kundens begäran. Denna process kan automatiseras om "
"(och när) betalningen online är :ref:`bekräftad <handling/sales>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:111
msgid ""
"To automate invoicing, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings` and in the :guilabel:`Invoicing` section, "
"enable :guilabel:`Automatic Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"För att automatisera fakturering, gå till :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` och i :guilabel:`Invoicing` avsnittet, "
"aktivera :guilabel:`Automatic Invoice`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:3
msgid "Payment providers"
msgstr "Betalningsleverantörer"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo supports a multitude of online :doc:`payment providers </applications/"
"finance/payment_providers>` for your website, allowing your customers to pay "
"with their preferred payment methods."
msgstr ""
"Odoo stöder en mängd online :doc:`betalningsleverantörer </applications/"
"finance/payment_providers>` för din webbplats, så att dina kunder kan betala "
"med sina föredragna betalningsmetoder."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:10
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:54
msgid ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:11
msgid ":doc:`checkout`"
msgstr ":doc:`utcheckning`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:14
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website.rst:28
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration.rst:5
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:21
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/reporting/link_tracker.rst:10
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguration"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:16
msgid ""
"To set up payment providers on the eCommerce app, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Payment Providers`. From "
"here, :guilabel:`Activate` the payment providers you wish to have available "
"on your shop, and configure them according to your needs."
msgstr ""
"För att ställa in betalningsleverantörer i e-handelsappen, gå "
"till :menuselection:`Webbplats --> Konfiguration --> "
"Betalningsleverantörer`. Härifrån :guilabel:`Aktivera` de "
"betalningsleverantörer som du vill ha tillgängliga i din butik och "
"konfigurera dem efter dina behov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:20
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can access **payment providers** "
"via :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Shop - Payment` section, you can :guilabel:`Configure SEPA "
"Direct Debit` if you wish to use it, as well as :guilabel:`View other "
"providers`. If you use the :guilabel:`Authorize.net` payment provider, "
"the :ref:`Payment Capture Method <payment_providers/manual_capture>` can be "
"configured in that same menu."
msgstr ""
"Alternativt kan du komma åt **betalningsleverantörer** "
"via :menuselection:`Webbplats --> Konfiguration --> Inställningar`. I "
"avsnittet :guilabel:`Shop - Payment` kan du :guilabel:`Konfigurera SEPA "
"Direct Debit` om du vill använda det, samt :guilabel:`Visa andra "
"leverantörer`. Om du använder :guilabel:`Authorize.net` "
"betalningsleverantör, kan :ref:`Payment Capture Method <payment_providers/"
"manual_capture>` konfigureras i samma meny."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:26
msgid ""
"If you are using :doc:`/applications/finance/payment_providers/paypal`, you "
"can also enable and configure it here."
msgstr ""
"Om du använder :doc:`/applications/finance/payment_providers/paypal` kan du "
"också aktivera och konfigurera det här."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:30
msgid "Checkout payment options"
msgstr "Betalningsalternativ för kassan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:32
msgid ""
"Once activated, customers can choose the payment provider of their choice "
"during the **checkout process**, at the :guilabel:`Confirm Order` step."
msgstr ""
"Efter aktivering kan kunderna välja vilken betalningsleverantör de vill "
"använda under **utcheckningsprocessen**, i steget :guilabel:`Confirm Order`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:None
msgid "Payment provider selection at checkout"
msgstr "Val av betalningsleverantör i kassan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:40
msgid "eWallets and gift cards"
msgstr "eWallets och presentkort"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:42
msgid ""
"When checking out, customers can pay with an eWallet or gift cards. To "
"enable these, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, "
"and in the :guilabel:`Shop-Products` section, "
"enable :menuselection:`Discounts, Loyalty & Gift Card`."
msgstr ""
"När kunderna checkar ut kan de betala med en e-plånbok eller presentkort. "
"För att aktivera dessa, gå till :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --"
"> Settings`, och i :guilabel:`Shop-Products` avsnittet, "
"aktivera :menuselection:`Discounts, Loyalty & Gift Card`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:46
msgid ""
"Once enabled, customers can enter their gift card **code** or pay with their "
"eWallet at the checkout step."
msgstr ""
"När detta är aktiverat kan kunderna ange presentkortets **kod** eller betala "
"med sin e-plånbok i kassan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:None
msgid "Enter gift card code to process checkout"
msgstr "Ange presentkortskod för att genomföra utcheckningen"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:3
msgid "Performance management"
msgstr "Prestandahantering"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo integrates a variety of tools to analyze and improve the performance of "
"your eCommerce website."
msgstr ""
"Odoo integrerar en mängd olika verktyg för att analysera och förbättra "
"prestandan på din e-handelswebbplats."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:9
msgid "Data monitoring"
msgstr "Övervakning av data"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:11
msgid ""
"**Website** allows monitoring and analysis of the sales performance of your "
"eCommerce. To access the **reporting view**, go to :menuselection:`Website --"
"> Reporting --> eCommerce`. This dashboard helps you monitor everything "
"related to sales, such as sales performance per product, category, day, etc."
msgstr ""
"Med **Webbplats** kan du övervaka och analysera försäljningsutvecklingen för "
"din e-handel. För att komma till **rapporteringsvyn**, gå "
"till :menuselection:`Webbplats --> Rapportering --> e-handel`. Denna "
"instrumentpanel hjälper dig att övervaka allt som rör försäljning, t.ex. "
"försäljningsresultat per produkt, kategori, dag osv."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:None
msgid "Performance reporting of eCommerce"
msgstr "Rapportering av prestanda för e-handel"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:19
msgid ""
"By clicking :guilabel:`Measures`, you can select the type of measurement "
"used, such as:"
msgstr ""
"Genom att klicka på :guilabel:`Mått` kan du välja vilken typ av mått som ska "
"användas, t.ex:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:21
msgid ":guilabel:`Margin`;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Margin`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:22
msgid ":guilabel:`Qty Invoiced`;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Fakturerat antal`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:23
msgid ":guilabel:`Untaxed Total`;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Oskattad totalsumma`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:24
msgid ":guilabel:`Volume`;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Volym`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:25
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:27
msgid ""
"Other options include **multiple views (Pivot, etc.), comparison** by "
"periods or years, and directly :guilabel:`insert in spreadsheet`, etc."
msgstr ""
"Andra alternativ inkluderar **flera vyer (Pivot, etc.), jämförelse** av "
"perioder eller år, och direkt :guilabel:`insert in spreadsheet`, etc."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:31
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:147
msgid "Analytics"
msgstr "Objekt"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:33
msgid ""
"It is possible to link your Odoo website with :ref:`analytics/plausible` "
"and :ref:`analytics/google-analytics`."
msgstr ""
"Det är möjligt att länka din Odoo-webbplats med :ref:`analytics/plausible` "
"och :ref:`analytics/google-analytics`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:39
msgid "Email queue optimization"
msgstr "Optimering av e-postkö"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:41
msgid ""
"For websites handling flash sales (e.g., event ticket sales) or experiencing "
"high traffic spikes, order confirmation emails can become a performance "
"bottleneck, potentially slowing down the checkout process for other "
"customers."
msgstr ""
"För hemsidor som hanterar snabbförsäljning (t.ex. försäljning av "
"evenemangsbiljetter) eller som upplever stora trafikspikar kan "
"orderbekräftelser via e-post bli en produktionsbegränsning som potentiellt "
"saktar ner kassaprocessen för andra kunder."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:45
msgid ""
"To improve performance, these emails can be queued and processed separately "
"from the order confirmation flow. This is managed by the :guilabel:`Sales: "
"Send pending emails` scheduled action, which sends queued emails as soon as "
"possible."
msgstr ""
"För att förbättra prestandan kan dessa e-postadresser köas och behandlas "
"separat från orderbekräftelseflödet. Detta hanteras av den schemalagda "
"åtgärden :guilabel:`F-örsäljning: Skicka väntande e-postadresser`, som "
"skickar köade e-postadresser så snart som möjligt."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:49
msgid "To enable asynchronous email sending:"
msgstr "Så här aktiverar du asynkron e-postsändning:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:51
msgid ""
"Enable the :doc:`developer mode </applications/general/developer_mode>`."
msgstr ""
"Aktivera :doc:`systemutvecklarläge </applications/general/developer_mode>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:52
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Apps`, remove the :guilabel:`Apps` filter, and install "
"the :guilabel:`Sales - Async Emails` module."
msgstr ""
"Gå till :menuselection:`Appar`, ta bort :guilabel:`Appar`-filtret och "
"installera modulen :guilabel:`Sales - Async Emails`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:54
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> System Parameters` and set "
"the :guilabel:`sale.async_emails` system parameter to `True`."
msgstr ""
"Gå till :menuselection:`Inställningar --> Technical --> System Parameters` "
"och ställ in systemparametern :guilabel:`sale.async_emails` till `True`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:56
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> Scheduled Actions` and "
"ensure that the :guilabel:`Sales: Send pending emails` scheduled action is "
"enabled."
msgstr ""
"Gå till :menuselection:`Inställningar --> Technical --> Scheduled Actions` "
"och se till att den schemalagda åtgärden :guilabel:`Sales: Send pending "
"emails` är aktiverad."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/performance.rst:60
msgid ""
"Enabling this feature may delay order confirmation and invoice emails by a "
"few minutes. It is recommended only for high-traffic websites, as it can "
"introduce unnecessary delays for e-commerce websites with moderate traffic."
msgstr ""
"Att aktivera den här funktionen kan fördröja orderbekräftelse- och fakturae-"
"postadresser med några minuter. Det rekommenderas endast för hemsidor med "
"hög trafik, eftersom det kan medföra onödiga förseningar för webbshoppar med "
"måttlig trafik."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:5
msgid "Products"
msgstr "Produkter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:7
msgid ""
"**Odoo eCommerce** allows you to :ref:`add products <ecommerce/products/add-"
"products>` and manage your :ref:`product pages <ecommerce/products/product-"
"page>` directly from the Website app. It also allows you to "
"add :ref:`product variants <ecommerce/products/product-variants>` "
"and :ref:`digital files <ecommerce/products/digital-"
"files>`, :ref:`translating <ecommerce/products/translation>` the product "
"page content, :ref:`managing stock <ecommerce/products/stock-management>`, "
"and enabling :ref:`product comparisons <ecommerce/products/product-"
"comparison>`."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo Webbshop** låter dig :ref:`lägga till produkter <ecommerce/products/"
"add-products>` och hantera dina :ref:`produktsidor <ecommerce/products/"
"product-page>` direkt från Hemsida-appen. Den låter dig också lägga till "
":ref:`produktvarianter <ecommerce/products/product-variants>` och "
":ref:`digitala filer <ecommerce/products/digital-files>`, :ref:`översätta "
"<ecommerce/products/translation>` produktsidans innehåll, :ref:`hantera "
"lager <ecommerce/products/stock-management>` och aktivera "
":ref:`produktjämförelser <ecommerce/products/product-comparison>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:18
msgid "Add products"
msgstr "Lägg till produkter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:23
msgid "Create products"
msgstr "Skapa produkter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:25
msgid ""
"To create a product from the frontend, click :guilabel:`+ New` in the top-"
"right corner, then :guilabel:`Product`. Enter the :guilabel:`Product "
"Name`, :guilabel:`Sales Price`, the default :guilabel:`Customer Taxes` for "
"local transactions, and :guilabel:`Save`. You can then update the product's "
"details, add an image, and :ref:`customize <ecommerce/products/"
"customization>` the product page. When you :guilabel:`Save`, the product "
"page is automatically published."
msgstr ""
"För att skapa en produkt från frontend, klicka på :guilabel:`+ New` i det "
"övre högra hörnet, sedan :guilabel:`Produkt`. Ange :guilabel:`Namn`, "
":guilabel:`Sales Price`, standard :guilabel:`Skatt knuten till kunder` för "
"lokala transaktioner och :guilabel:`Spara`. Du kan sedan uppgradera "
"produktens detaljer, lägga till en bild och :ref:`specialanpassa <ecommerce/"
"products/customization>` produktsidan. När du :guilabel:`Spara`, publiceras "
"produktsidan automatiskt."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:32
msgid ""
"You can also create a product from the backend by going "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products` and "
"clicking :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Du kan också skapa en produkt från backend genom att gå till "
":menuselection:`Hemsida --> Webbshop --> Produkter` och klicka på "
":guilabel:`New`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:34
msgid ""
"Products created from the frontend are automatically :ref:`published "
"<website/pages/un-publish-page>`, while products created from the backend "
"are not. To publish a product, click the :guilabel:`Go to Website` smart "
"button to access the product page, then toggle the switch "
"from :guilabel:`Unpublished` to :guilabel:`Published`."
msgstr ""
"Produkter som skapas från frontend :ref:`publiceras <website/pages/un-"
"publish-page>` automatiskt, medan produkter som skapas från backend inte gör "
"det. För att publicera en produkt, klicka på den smarta knappen "
":guilabel:`Go to Website` för att komma åt produktsidan, växla sedan "
"omkopplaren från :guilabel:`Unpublished` till :guilabel:`Published`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:40
msgid ""
":doc:`Create new products using the Barcode Lookup database </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/barcode/setup/barcodelookup>`."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Skapa nya produkter med hjälp av databasen Streckkodssökning </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/setup/barcodelookup>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:46
msgid "Import products"
msgstr "Importprodukter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:48
msgid ""
"To :ref:`import product data <essentials/export_import_data/import-data>` "
"using XLSX or CSV files, go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> "
"Products`, click the :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`gear`) icon, "
"then :ref:`Import records <essentials/export_import_data/import-data>`."
msgstr ""
"För att :ref:`importera produktdata <essentials/export_import_data/import-"
"data>` med XLSX- eller CSV-filer, gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> "
"Webbshop --> Produkter`, klicka på :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`gear`) ikonen, "
"sedan :ref:`Importera handlingar <essentials/export_import_data/import-data>"
"`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:53
msgid "To publish **large batches** of products, follow these steps:"
msgstr "För att publicera **stora partier** av produkter, följ dessa steg:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:55
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products`."
msgstr "Gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> Webbshop --> Produkter`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:56
msgid ""
"Remove the :guilabel:`Published` filter and switch to the :guilabel:`List` "
"view."
msgstr ""
"Ta bort filtret :guilabel:`Publicerad` och växla till vyn :guilabel:`Lista`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:57
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-sliders` (:guilabel:`dropdown toggle`) icon and "
"enable :guilabel:`Is published`."
msgstr ""
"Klicka på :icon:`fa-sliders` (:guilabel:`rullgardinsmeny`) ikonen och "
"aktivera :guilabel:`Is published`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:59
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Is Published` column to re-order it by **published** or "
"**unpublished** products."
msgstr ""
"Klicka på kolumnen :guilabel:`Is Published` för att ordna om den efter "
"**publicerade** eller **opublicerade** produkter."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:61
msgid "Select the products to publish by ticking their box."
msgstr "Välj de produkter som ska publiceras genom att markera deras ruta."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:62
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Is Published` column, tick the box for any of the selected "
"products, then :guilabel:`Confirm` to publish them."
msgstr ""
"I kolumnen :guilabel:`Is Published`, markera rutan för någon av de valda "
"produkterna, sedan :guilabel:`Bekräfta` för att publicera dem."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:68
msgid "Product page customization"
msgstr "Specialanpassning av produktsida"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:73
msgid "Product information"
msgstr "Information om produkten"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:76
msgid ""
"To add general information about a product, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products` and select the "
"product. You can configure the product page from the form by "
"adding :ref:`variants <ecommerce/products/product-variants>`, :ref:`digital "
"documents <ecommerce/products/digital-files>`, or :ref:`translating "
"<ecommerce/products/translation>` content."
msgstr ""
"För att lägga till allmän information om en produkt, navigera till "
":menuselection:`Hemsida --> Webbshop --> Produkter` och välj produkten. Du "
"kan konfigurera produktsidan från formuläret genom att lägga till "
":ref:`varianter <ecommerce/products/product-variants>`, :ref:`digitala "
"dokument <ecommerce/products/digital-files>` eller :ref:`översätta "
"<ecommerce/products/translation>` innehåll."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:81
msgid ""
"You can also add an ecommerce-specific product description to be displayed "
"below the product name on the product's page. To do so, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Ecommerce "
"description` section, and add a description. Use Odoo's :doc:`rich-text "
"editor <../../essentials/html_editor>` features to personalize the content."
msgstr ""
"Du kan också lägga till en webbshopsspecifik produktbeskrivning som ska "
"visas under produktnamnet på produktens sida. För att göra detta, gå till "
"fliken :guilabel:`Försäljning`, scrolla ner till avsnittet "
":guilabel:`Webbshopsbeskrivning` och lägg till en beskrivning. Använd Odoos "
":doc:`rich-text-redigerare <../../essentials/html_editor>` för att "
"personalisera innehållet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:87
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Go to Website` smart button to return to the frontend "
"product's page."
msgstr ""
"Klicka på smart knappen :guilabel:`Gå till hemsida` för att återgå till "
"produktsidan på frontend."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:92
msgid "Product presentation"
msgstr "Produktpresentation"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:94
msgid ""
"To customize the product presentation on the website, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Shop` and click on the product. Click :guilabel:`Edit` "
"to :ref:`customize <ecommerce/products/customization>` the page, :ref:`edit "
"its images <ecommerce/products/image-customization>` or add :doc:`building "
"blocks <../../websites/website/web_design/building_blocks>`."
msgstr ""
"För att specialanpassa produktpresentationen på hemsidan, gå till "
":guilabel:`Butiken` och klicka på produkten. Klicka på :guilabel:`Redigera` "
"för att :ref:`specialanpassa <ecommerce/products/customization>` sidan, "
":ref:`redigera dess bilder <ecommerce/products/image-customization>` eller "
"lägg till :doc:`byggmoduler <../../websites/website/web_design/"
"building_blocks>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:100
msgid ""
"When dragging and dropping a building block on the product page, placing it "
"above or below the top or bottom blue lines makes it visible on all product "
"pages."
msgstr ""
"När du drar och släpper en byggmodul på produktsidan gör det den synlig på "
"alla produktsidor om du placerar den ovanför eller under de översta eller "
"nedersta blå linjerna."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:102
msgid ""
"You can edit any text on your website by clicking on it while "
"in :guilabel:`Edit` mode."
msgstr ""
"Du kan redigera vilken text som helst på din hemsida genom att klicka på den "
"när du är i :guilabel:`Redigera`-läge."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:104
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Customize` tab to modify the page layout or add features:"
msgstr ""
"Använd fliken :guilabel:`Specialanpassa` för att ändra sidlayouten eller "
"lägga till funktioner:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:106
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Terms and Conditions`: Toggle the switch to display a link to "
"your :doc:`terms and conditions <../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices/"
"terms_conditions>` on the product page."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Villkor`: Aktivera växeln för att visa en länk till dina "
":doc:`villkor <../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices/terms_conditions>` "
"på produktsidan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:110
msgid ":guilabel:`Customers`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Kunder`:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:112
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Rating`: Allow logged-in portal users to submit product reviews "
"by clicking the stars below the product's name and sharing their experience "
"in the :guilabel:`Customer Reviews` section at the bottom. Reviews are "
"visible from the product page using the :icon:`fa-plus` (:guilabel:`plus`) "
"icon next to the :guilabel:`Customer Reviews` heading or from the product "
"form's chatter. To restrict visibility to internal employees, toggle "
"the :guilabel:`Public` switch next to the review comment."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Betyg`: Tillåt inloggade portalanvändare att skicka in "
"produktrecensioner genom att klicka på stjärnorna under produktens namn och "
"dela sina erfarenheter i avsnittet :guilabel:`Kundrecensioner` längst ner. "
"Recensioner är synliga från produktsidan med hjälp av ikonen :icon:`fa-plus` "
"(:guilabel:`plus`) bredvid rubriken :guilabel:`Kundrecensioner` eller från "
"produktformulärets händelseflöde. För att begränsa synligheten till interna "
"anställda, aktivera växeln :guilabel:`Offentlig` bredvid "
"recensionskommentaren."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:118
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Share`: Add social media and email icon buttons allowing "
"customers to share the product through those channels."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dela`: Lägg till knappar för sociala medier och e-post som gör "
"det möjligt för kunder att dela produkten via dessa kanaler."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:121
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Select Quantity`: Toggle the switch to allow customers to select "
"the product quantity they want to purchase."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Välj antal`: Aktivera växeln för att tillåta kunder att välja den "
"produktkvantitet de vill köpa."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:124
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tax Indication`: Toggle the switch to indicate if the price "
"is :ref:`VAT included or excluded <ecommerce/prices/taxes>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Momsindikering`: Slå på växlingsknappen för att ange om priset är "
":ref:`inklusive eller exklusive moms <ecommerce/prices/taxes>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:127
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Variants`: Show all possible product :ref:`variants <ecommerce/"
"products/product-variants>` vertically as a :guilabel:`Products List` or "
"horizontally as selectable :guilabel:`Options` to compose the variant "
"yourself."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Varianter`: Visa alla möjliga produkt :ref:`varianter <ecommerce/"
"products/product-variants>` vertikalt som en :guilabel:`Produktlista` eller "
"horisontellt som valbara :guilabel:`Optioner` för att själv komponera "
"varianten."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:131
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product Tags`: Toggle the switch to display "
"the :guilabel:`Product Template Tags` on the product page and allow "
"customers to filter products using those tags."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Produkttaggar`: Aktivera växeln för att visa "
":guilabel:`Produktmallstaggar` på produktsidan och tillåta kunder att "
"filtrera produkter med hjälp av dessa taggar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:134
msgid ":guilabel:`Cart`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Varukorg`:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:136
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Buy Now`: Add a :icon:`fa-bolt` :guilabel:`Buy Now` option to "
"take the customer to the checkout page."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Köp nu`: Lägg till ett :icon:`fa-bolt` :guilabel:`Köp nu`-"
"alternativ för att ta kunden till kassan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:138
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Wishlist`: Add an :icon:`fa-heart-o` :guilabel:`Add to wishlist` "
"option allowing logged-in customers to save products in a wishlist."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Önskelista`: Lägg till ett :icon:`fa-heart-o` :guilabel:`Lägg "
"till i önskelista` alternativ som gör det möjligt för inloggade kunder att "
"spara produkter i en önskelista."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:140
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Compare`: Add a :icon:`fa-exchange` :guilabel:`Compare` option, "
"allowing customers to :ref:`compare products <ecommerce/products/product-"
"comparison>` based on their attributes."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jämför`: Lägg till ett :icon:`fa-exchange` :guilabel:`Jämför` "
"alternativ som gör det möjligt för kunder att :ref:`jämföra produkter "
"<ecommerce/products/product-comparison>` baserat på deras attribut."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:143
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Specification`: Select :guilabel:`Bottom of Page` to display a "
"detailed list of the attributes and their values available for the product. "
"This option only works for products with :ref:`variants <ecommerce/products/"
"product-variants>` if the :ref:`Product comparison tool <ecommerce/products/"
"product-comparison>` is enabled in the Website :guilabel:`Settings`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Specifikation`: Välj :guilabel:`Nederkant av sidan` för att visa "
"en detaljerad lista över attributen och deras värden som är tillgängliga för "
"produkten. Detta alternativ fungerar endast för produkter med "
":ref:`varianter <ecommerce/products/product-variants>` om "
":ref:`Produktjämförelseverktyget <ecommerce/products/product-comparison>` är "
"aktiverat i webbplatsens :guilabel:`Inställningar`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:150
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Variants`, :icon:`fa-heart-o` :guilabel:`Wishlist`, and :icon:`fa-"
"exchange` :guilabel:`Compare` options must be enabled by going "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, in "
"the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Varianter`, :icon:`fa-heart-o` :guilabel:`Önskelista`, och "
":icon:`fa-exchange` :guilabel:`Jämför` alternativ måste aktiveras genom att "
"gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> Konfiguration --> Inställningar`, i "
":guilabel:`Butik - Produkter` sektionen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:154
msgid "Enabled functions apply to all product pages."
msgstr "Aktiverade funktioner gäller för alla produktsidor."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:155
msgid ""
"Products with single values for their attributes do not generate variants "
"but are still displayed in the :guilabel:`Product Specifications`."
msgstr ""
"Produkter med enstaka värden för sina attribut genererar inte varianter men "
"visas ändå i :guilabel:`Produktspecifikationer`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:161
msgid "Product images and videos"
msgstr "Produktbilder och videor"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:163
msgid ""
"To add more media items, such as images and videos, navigate to "
"the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/products/product-form>`, then go to "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` tab and click :guilabel:`Add Media` under "
"the :guilabel:`Ecommerce Media` section. In the :guilabel:`Select a media` "
"pop-up window, go to the :guilabel:`Images` tab, select an image, "
"click :guilabel:`Upload an image` or :guilabel:`Add URL`. Or navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Videos` tab, paste a video URL or embed code. Once done, "
"click :guilabel:`Add`."
msgstr ""
"För att lägga till fler medieobjekt, såsom bilder och videor, navigera till "
":ref:`produktformuläret <ecommerce/products/product-form>`, gå sedan till "
"fliken :guilabel:`Försäljning` och klicka på :guilabel:`Lägg till media` "
"under :guilabel:`Webbshopsmedia` sektionen. I popup-fönstret :guilabel:`Välj "
"ett media`, gå till fliken :guilabel:`Bilder`, välj en bild, klicka på "
":guilabel:`Ladda upp en bild` eller :guilabel:`Lägg till URL`. Eller "
"navigera till fliken :guilabel:`Videor`, klistra in en video-URL eller "
"inbäddningskod. När du är klar, klicka på :guilabel:`Lägg till`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:170
msgid ""
"To customize the images or videos, go to the ecommerce product page, "
"click :guilabel:`Edit` and select the relevant media. In "
"the :guilabel:`Customize` tab, use the following features:"
msgstr ""
"För att anpassa bilderna eller videorna, gå till webbshopsproduktsidan, "
"klicka på :guilabel:`Redigera` och välj relevant media. I fliken "
":guilabel:`Anpassa`, använd följande funktioner:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:173
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Images Width`: Changes the width of the product images displayed "
"on the page."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bildbredd`: Ändrar bredden på produktbilderna som visas på sidan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:174
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Layout`: The :guilabel:`Carousel` layout allows customers to "
"navigate from one image to the next using the :icon:`fa-angle-left` "
"(:guilabel:`left arrow`) or :icon:`fa-angle-right` (:guilabel:`right "
"arrow`); whereas the :guilabel:`Grid` displays four images in a square "
"layout."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Layout`: :guilabel:`Karusell` layouten gör det möjligt för kunder "
"att navigera från en bild till nästa med hjälp av :icon:`fa-angle-left` "
"(:guilabel:`vänsterpil`) eller :icon:`fa-angle-right` (:guilabel:`högerpil`)"
"; medan :guilabel:`Rutnät` visar fyra bilder i en fyrkantig layout."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:177
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Image Zoom`: Select the zoom effect for product "
"images: :guilabel:`Magnifier on hover` :guilabel:`Pop-up on "
"Click`, :guilabel:`Both`, or :guilabel:`None`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bildzoom`: Välj zoomeffekten för produktbilder: "
":guilabel:`Förstoringsglas vid hovring` :guilabel:`Popup vid klick`, "
":guilabel:`Båda`, eller :guilabel:`Ingen`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:179
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Thumbnails`: Align thumbnails on the :icon:`fa-long-arrow-left` "
"(:guilabel:`Left`) or at the :icon:`fa-long-arrow-down` (:guilabel:`Bottom`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Miniatyrbilder`: Justera miniatyrbilderna på :icon:`fa-long-arrow-"
"left` (:guilabel:`Vänster`) eller vid :icon:`fa-long-arrow-down` "
"(:guilabel:`Nederkant`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:182
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Main Image`: Click :guilabel:`Replace` to change the product's "
"main image."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Huvudbild`: Klicka på :guilabel:`Ersätt` för att ändra produktens "
"huvudbild."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:183
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Extra Images`: :guilabel:`Add` more extra images or videos "
"(including via URL) or :guilabel:`Remove all`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Extra bilder`: :guilabel:`Lägg till` fler extra bilder eller "
"videor (inklusive via URL) eller :guilabel:`Ta bort alla`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:187
msgid ""
"Images must be in PNG or JPG format, with at least one dimension (height or "
"width) greater than 1024 pixels to trigger the zoom."
msgstr ""
"Bilder måste vara i PNG- eller JPG-format, med åtminstone en dimension (höjd "
"eller bredd) större än 1024 pixlar för att utlösa zoom."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:193
msgid "Products block"
msgstr "Produktmodul"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:195
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Products` :doc:`building block <../website/web_design/"
"building_blocks>` is used to display a selection of products sold on your "
"website."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Produkter` :doc:`byggmodulen <../website/web_design/"
"building_blocks>` används för att visa ett urval av produkter som säljs på "
"din webbplats."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:None
msgid "Example of a products block"
msgstr "Exempel på ett produktblock"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:201
msgid ""
"By default, the block displays the :guilabel:`Newest Products`. To change "
"which products are shown, go to the :guilabel:`Customize` "
"tab's :guilabel:`Products` section and set the :guilabel:`Filter` field "
"to :guilabel:`Recently Sold Products` or :guilabel:`Recently Viewed "
"Products`."
msgstr ""
"Som standard visar modulen :guilabel:`Nyaste produkter`. För att ändra vilka "
"produkter som visas, gå till fliken :guilabel:`Anpassa` i "
":guilabel:`Produkter` sektionen och ställ in fältet :guilabel:`Filter` till "
":guilabel:`Nyligen sålda produkter` eller :guilabel:`Nyligen visade "
"produkter`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:205
msgid ""
"In addition, it is possible to display products from a specific category "
"only using the :guilabel:`Category` field."
msgstr ""
"Dessutom är det möjligt att visa produkter från endast en specifik kategori "
"genom att använda fältet :guilabel:`Kategori`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:208
msgid ""
"You can also filter products by :guilabel:`Tags`, "
"include :guilabel:`Variants`, and adjust the display by selecting a "
"different :guilabel:`Template`."
msgstr ""
"Du kan också filtrera produkter efter :guilabel:`Taggar`, inkludera "
":guilabel:`Varianter`, och justera visningen genom att välja en annan "
":guilabel:`Mall`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:214
msgid "Product variants"
msgstr "Produktvarianter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:216
msgid ""
":doc:`Product variants <../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/"
"variants>` are different versions of the same product, such as various "
"colors or materials, with potential differences in price and availability."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Produktvarianter <../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants>"
"` är olika versioner av samma produkt, såsom olika färger eller material, "
"med potentiella skillnader i pris och tillgänglighet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:220
msgid "To configure product variants for a product:"
msgstr "Så här konfigurerar du produktvarianter för en produkt:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:222
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:104
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:26
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:136
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""
"Gå till :menuselection:`Webbplats --> Konfiguration --> Inställningar`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:223
msgid ""
"Scroll down to the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section and enable "
"the :guilabel:`Product Variants` feature."
msgstr ""
"Rulla ner till sektionen :guilabel:`Butik - Produkter` och aktivera "
"funktionen :guilabel:`Produktvarianter`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:225
msgid ""
"Access the :ref:`product forms <ecommerce/products/product-form>` and go to "
"the :guilabel:`Attributes & Variants` tab, where you can add attributes and "
"values, allowing customers to configure and select product variants on the "
"product page. For multiple attributes, you can combine them to create "
"specific variants."
msgstr ""
"Öppna :ref:`produktformulären <ecommerce/products/product-form>` och gå till "
"fliken :guilabel:`Attribut & Varianter`, där du kan lägga till attribut och "
"värden som gör det möjligt för kunder att konfigurera och välja "
"produktvarianter på produktsidan. För flera attribut kan du kombinera dem "
"för att skapa specifika varianter."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:230
msgid ""
"To display or hide an attribute on the :guilabel:`Shop` page and allow "
"visitors to filter them, go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> "
"Attributes`, click on the attribute, and select :guilabel:`Visible` "
"or :guilabel:`Hidden` in the :guilabel:`eCommerce Filter Visibility` field."
msgstr ""
"För att visa eller dölja ett attribut på sidan :guilabel:`Butik` och låta "
"besökare filtrera dem, gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> Webbshop --> "
"Attribut`, klicka på attributet och välj :guilabel:`Synlig` eller "
":guilabel:`Dold` i fältet :guilabel:`Webbshop Filtersynlighet`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:235
msgid ""
"To display the product attributes in the :doc:`product catalog <products/"
"catalog>`, set the :guilabel:`Attributes` feature to :guilabel:`Left` using "
"the website editor."
msgstr ""
"För att visa produktattributen i :doc:`produktkatalogen <products/catalog>`, "
"ställ in funktionen :guilabel:`Attribut` till :guilabel:`Vänster` med hjälp "
"av hemsideredigeraren."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:237
msgid ""
"To group attributes under the same section when :ref:`comparing products "
"<ecommerce/products/product-comparison>`, go to the :guilabel:`eCommerce "
"Category` field and either select an :doc:`existing category or create a new "
"one <../../websites/ecommerce/products>`."
msgstr ""
"För att gruppera attribut under samma sektion när du :ref:`jämför produkter "
"<ecommerce/products/product-comparison>`, gå till fältet :guilabel:`Webbshop "
"Kategori` och välj antingen en :doc:`befintlig kategori eller skapa en ny "
"<../../websites/ecommerce/products>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:243
msgid "Two attribute values are needed to make the filter visible."
msgstr "Två attributvärden behövs för att göra filtret synligt."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:246
msgid ""
":doc:`Product variants <../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Produktvarianter <../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:251
msgid "Digital files"
msgstr "Digitala filer"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:253
msgid ""
"You can link digital files like certificates, eBooks, or user manuals to the "
"products. These documents are available :ref:`before payment <ecommerce-"
"products-digital-files-before-payment>` on the product page or in the "
"customer portal :ref:`after checkout <ecommerce-products-digital-files-after-"
"payment>`."
msgstr ""
"Du kan länka digitala filer som certifikat, e-böcker eller "
"användarhandböcker till produkterna. Dessa dokument är tillgängliga "
":ref:`före betalning <ecommerce-products-digital-files-before-payment>` på "
"produktsidan eller i kundportalen :ref:`efter utcheckning <ecommerce-"
"products-digital-files-after-payment>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:258
msgid ""
"To link a digital file to a product, go to the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/"
"products/product-form>` and click the :guilabel:`Documents` smart button. "
"Then, click :guilabel:`Upload` to upload a file directly, or for additional "
"options, click :guilabel:`New`, then :guilabel:`Upload your file`."
msgstr ""
"För att länka en digital fil till en produkt, gå till "
":ref:`produktformuläret <ecommerce/products/product-form>` och klicka på den "
"smarta knappen :guilabel:`Dokument`. Klicka sedan på :guilabel:`Ladda upp` "
"för att ladda upp en fil direkt, eller för ytterligare optioner, klicka på "
":guilabel:`Ny` och sedan :guilabel:`Ladda upp din fil`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:263
msgid ""
"You can link a URL instead of a digital file. To do so, "
"click :guilabel:`New`, go to the :guilabel:`Type` field, and "
"select :guilabel:`URL`."
msgstr ""
"Du kan länka en URL istället för en digital fil. För att göra detta, klicka "
"på :guilabel:`Ny`, gå till fältet :guilabel:`Typ` och välj :guilabel:`URL`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:265
msgid ""
"To edit an existing file, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
"(:guilabel:`dropdown menu`) in the top-right corner of the document card and "
"click :guilabel:`Edit`."
msgstr ""
"För att redigera en befintlig fil, klicka på :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
"(:guilabel:`rullgardinsmeny`) i övre högra hörnet av dokumentkortet och "
"klicka på :guilabel:`Redigera`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:271
msgid "Digital files available before payment"
msgstr "Digitala filer tillgängliga före betalning"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:273
msgid ""
"To make the file available on the product page (before payment), leave "
"the :guilabel:`Visibility` field blank and toggle the :guilabel:`Show on "
"product page` switch."
msgstr ""
"För att göra filen tillgänglig på produktsidan (före betalning), lämna "
"fältet :guilabel:`Synlighet` tomt och aktivera växeln :guilabel:`Visa på "
"produktsida`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:None
msgid "digital file available before payment on the  product page"
msgstr "digital fil tillgänglig före betalning på produktsidan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:282
msgid "Digital files available after payment"
msgstr "Digitala filer tillgängliga efter betalning"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:284
msgid ""
"To make the file available (after payment), set the :guilabel:`Visibility` "
"field to :guilabel:`Confirmed order` and turn off the :guilabel:`Show on "
"product page` switch."
msgstr ""
"För att göra filen tillgänglig (efter betalning), ställ in fältet "
":guilabel:`Synlighet` till :guilabel:`Bekräftad beställning` och stäng av "
"växeln :guilabel:`Visa på produktsida`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:290
msgid "Translation"
msgstr "Översättning"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:292
msgid ""
"If multiple languages are available on your website, you can translate a "
"product's information directly on the :ref:`product form <ecommerce/products/"
"product-form>`. Fields that support multiple languages are identifiable by "
"their abbreviation language (e.g., EN) next to their field."
msgstr ""
"Om flera språk är tillgängliga på din hemsida kan du översätta en produkts "
"information direkt i :ref:`produktformuläret <ecommerce/products/product-"
"form>`. Fält som stöder flera språk kan identifieras genom sin "
"språkförkortning (t.ex. SV) bredvid fältet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:296
msgid "The eCommerce-related fields to translate are:"
msgstr "De webbshopsrelaterade fälten att översätta är:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:298
msgid ":guilabel:`Product name`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Produktnamn`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:299
msgid ":guilabel:`Out-of-Stock Message` (under the :guilabel:`Sales` tab)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Meddelande vid slut i lager` (under fliken "
":guilabel:`Försäljning`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:300
msgid ":guilabel:`Sales Description` (under the :guilabel:`Sales` tab)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Försäljningsbeskrivning` (under fliken :guilabel:`Försäljning`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:303
msgid ""
"Having untranslated content on a web page may be detrimental to the user "
"experience and :doc:`SEO <../../websites/website/structure/seo>`. You can "
"use the :doc:`Translate <../website/configuration/translate>` feature to "
"translate the page's content."
msgstr ""
"Att ha oöversatt innehåll på en webbsida kan vara skadligt för "
"användarupplevelsen och :doc:`Sökmotoroptimering <../../websites/website/"
"structure/seo>`. Du kan använda funktionen :doc:`Översätt <../website/"
"configuration/translate>` för att översätta sidans innehåll."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:306
msgid ""
"To check the language(s) of your website, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` and go to the :guilabel:`Website Info` section."
msgstr ""
"För att kontrollera språket/språken på din hemsida, gå till "
":menuselection:`Hemsida --> Konfiguration --> Inställningar` och gå till "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Webbplatsinformation`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:312
msgid "Website availability"
msgstr "Tillgänglighet på webbplatsen"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:314
msgid ""
"To set the product's website availability, navigate to the :ref:`product "
"form <ecommerce/products/product-form>`, go to the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, "
"and in the :guilabel:`eCommerce shop` section, select "
"the :guilabel:`Website` you wish the product to be available on. Leave the "
"field blank to make the product available on *all* websites."
msgstr ""
"För att ställa in produktens tillgänglighet på hemsidan, navigera till "
":ref:`produktformuläret <ecommerce/products/product-form>`, gå till fliken "
":guilabel:`Försäljning`, och i sektionen :guilabel:`Webbshop`, välj den "
":guilabel:`Hemsida` du vill att produkten ska vara tillgänglig på. Lämna "
"fältet tomt för att göra produkten tillgänglig på *alla* hemsidor."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:320
msgid ""
"You can make a product available on either *one* website or *all* websites, "
"but selecting only *some* websites is not possible."
msgstr ""
"Du kan göra en produkt tillgänglig på antingen *en* hemsida eller *alla* "
"hemsidor, men att välja endast *vissa* hemsidor är inte möjligt."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:326
msgid "Stock management"
msgstr "Lagerförvaltning"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:328
msgid ""
"To enable and configure inventory management options, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section and the :guilabel:`Inventory "
"Defaults` sub-section."
msgstr ""
"För att aktivera och konfigurera lagerhanteringsoptioner, gå till "
":menuselection:`Hemsida --> Konfiguration --> Inställningar`, scrolla ner "
"till sektionen :guilabel:`Butik - Produkter` och undersektionen "
":guilabel:`Lager standardinställningar`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:333
msgid ""
"The **Inventory** app must be installed to see the inventory management "
"options."
msgstr ""
"Appen **Lager** måste vara installerad för att se lagerhanteringsoptionerna."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:334
msgid ""
"To display the stock level on the product page, the :guilabel:`Product Type` "
"field must be set to :guilabel:`Storable` in the :ref:`product form "
"<ecommerce/products/product-form>`."
msgstr ""
"För att visa lagernivån på produktsidan måste fältet :guilabel:`Produkttyp` "
"vara inställt på :guilabel:`Lagringsbar` i :ref:`produktformuläret "
"<ecommerce/products/product-form>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:338
msgid "Inventory"
msgstr "Inventering"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:340
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Inventory Defaults` sub-section, fill in those fields:"
msgstr ""
"I undersektionen :guilabel:`Lager standardinställningar`, fyll i dessa fält:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:342
msgid ""
":doc:`Warehouse <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/"
"inventory_management/warehouses>`."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Lager <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/"
"inventory_management/warehouses>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:343
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Out-of-Stock`: Enable :guilabel:`Continue Selling` to allow "
"customers to place orders even when the product is **out of stock**. Leave "
"the box unchecked to **prevent orders**."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Slut i lager`: Aktivera :guilabel:`Fortsätt sälja` för att "
"tillåta kunder att lägga beställningar även när produkten är **slut i "
"lager**. Lämna rutan okryssad för att **förhindra beställningar**."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:345
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Show Available Qty`: Displays the available quantity left under a "
"specified threshold on the product page. The available quantity is "
"calculated based on the :guilabel:`On hand` quantity minus the quantity "
"already reserved for outgoing transfers."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Visa tillgängligt antal`: Visar det tillgängliga antalet kvar "
"under ett angivet tröskelvärde på produktsidan. Det tillgängliga antalet "
"beräknas baserat på antalet :guilabel:`I lager` minus det antal som redan är "
"reserverat för utgående överföringar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:352
msgid "Product comparison"
msgstr "Jämförelse av produkter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:354
msgid ""
"To allow website visitors to compare products based on their attributes, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section, and enable :guilabel:`Product "
"Comparison Tool`."
msgstr ""
"För att låta besökare på hemsidan jämföra produkter baserat på deras "
"attribut, gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> Konfiguration --> "
"Inställningar`, scrolla ner till sektionen :guilabel:`Butik - Produkter`, "
"och aktivera :guilabel:`Produktjämförelseverktyg`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:358
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Compare`) icon is now available on each "
"product card on the main shop page when customers hover their mouse over it. "
"To compare products, customers can click the :icon:`fa-exchange` "
"(:guilabel:`Compare`) option on the products they want to compare, then "
"click :icon:`fa-exchange` :guilabel:`Compare` in the pop-up window at the "
"bottom of the page to reach the comparison summary."
msgstr ""
"Ikonen :icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Jämför`) är nu tillgänglig på varje "
"produktkort på huvudbutikssidan när kunder håller musen över den. För att "
"jämföra produkter kan kunder klicka på alternativet :icon:`fa-exchange` "
"(:guilabel:`Jämför`) på de produkter de vill jämföra, sedan klicka på "
":icon:`fa-exchange` :guilabel:`Jämför` i popup-fönstret längst ner på sidan "
"för att nå jämförelsesammanfattningen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:None
msgid "Product comparison window"
msgstr "Fönster för produktjämförelse"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:368
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Product Comparison Tool` is only available for products "
"with :ref:`attributes <ecommerce/products/product-variants>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Produktjämförelseverktyget` är endast tillgängligt för produkter "
"med :ref:`attribut <ecommerce/products/product-variants>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:370
msgid ""
"Selecting the :icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Compare`) option from a "
"product page is also possible."
msgstr ""
"Att välja alternativet :icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Jämför`) från en "
"produktsida är också möjligt."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:376
msgid "Wishlists"
msgstr "Önskelistor"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:378
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-heart-o` :guilabel:`Add to wishlist` button allows customers "
"to add products to their wishlist, i.e., save them for later. To enable it, "
"go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down "
"to the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section, and "
"enable :guilabel:`Wishlists`. The button is available on each product page "
"and can be disabled in the :ref:`website editor <ecommerce/products/product-"
"page>` if needed."
msgstr ""
"Knappen :icon:`fa-heart-o` :guilabel:`Lägg till i önskelista` gör det "
"möjligt för kunder att lägga till produkter i sin önskelista, dvs. spara dem "
"för senare. För att aktivera den, gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> "
"Konfiguration --> Inställningar`, rulla ner till sektionen "
":guilabel:`Butik - Produkter` och aktivera :guilabel:`Önskelistor`. Knappen "
"är tillgänglig på varje produktsida och kan avaktiveras i "
":ref:`hemsideredigeraren <ecommerce/products/product-page>` vid behov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:None
msgid "Add to wishlist button"
msgstr "Lägg till i önskelista-knapp"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:388
msgid ""
"You can also display a :icon:`fa-heart-o` (:guilabel:`Wishlist`) button when "
"hovering the mouse over the product on the :ref:`shop page <ecommerce/"
"catalog/additional-features>`."
msgstr ""
"Du kan också visa en :icon:`fa-heart-o` (:guilabel:`Önskelista`)-knapp när "
"du för musen över produkten på :ref:`butikssidan <ecommerce/catalog/"
"additional-features>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:390
msgid ""
"Customers can move products from their cart to their wishlist by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Save for later` button in the :guilabel:`Order "
"overview` :ref:`checkout step <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>`."
msgstr ""
"Kunder kan flytta produkter från sin kundvagn till sin önskelista genom att "
"klicka på knappen :guilabel:`Spara för senare` i "
":guilabel:`Beställningsöversikt` :ref:`kassan <ecommerce/checkout/"
"review_order>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:3
msgid "Catalog"
msgstr "Katalog"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:5
msgid ""
"The eCommerce catalog displays products for customers to browse. It is "
"organized using product categories, available options, sorting, and "
"navigation paths. Essentially, the eCommerce catalog is the shop page of "
"your website."
msgstr ""
"Webbshopskatalogen visar produkter för kunder att bläddra bland. Den är "
"organiserad med hjälp av produktkategorier, tillgängliga alternativ, "
"sortering och navigeringsvägar. I grund och botten är webbshopskatalogen "
"butikssidan på din hemsida."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:9
msgid ""
"The product catalog includes a :ref:`top bar <ecommerce/catalog/top-bar>`, "
"a :ref:`side panel <ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>`, and a :ref:`product "
"listing area <ecommerce/catalog/product-listing>`. With Odoo, you "
"can :ref:`customize the layout <ecommerce/catalog/customize-layout>`, filter "
"by :ref:`categories and attributes <ecommerce/catalog/categories>`, and "
"use :ref:`additional features <ecommerce/catalog/additional-features>` "
"according to your needs."
msgstr ""
"Produktkatalogen inkluderar en :ref:`översta raden <ecommerce/catalog/top-"
"bar>`, ett :ref:`sidofält <ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>` och ett "
":ref:`produktlistningsområde <ecommerce/catalog/product-listing>`. Med Odoo "
"kan du :ref:`anpassa layouten <ecommerce/catalog/customize-layout>`, "
"filtrera efter :ref:`kategorier och attribut <ecommerce/catalog/categories>` "
"och använda :ref:`ytterligare funktioner <ecommerce/catalog/additional-"
"features>` enligt dina behov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:16
msgid ""
"You can customize the shop page using the website editor. To access it, go "
"to the shop page, click :guilabel:`Edit` in the upper-right corner, and "
"navigate to the :guilabel:`Customize` tab."
msgstr ""
"Du kan anpassa butikssidan med hjälp av hemsideredigeraren. För att komma åt "
"den, gå till butikssidan, klicka på :guilabel:`Redigera` i övre högra hörnet "
"och navigera till fliken :guilabel:`Anpassa`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:22
msgid "Top bar"
msgstr "Översta baren"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:24
msgid ""
"The top bar can include a search bar, a currency selector, :ref:`sort-by and "
"display options <ecommerce/catalog/sort-by-and-display-option>`, "
"and :ref:`category quick access <ecommerce/catalog/categories>`."
msgstr ""
"Den översta raden kan inkludera en sökfält, en valutaväljare, :ref:`sortera-"
"efter och visningsalternativ <ecommerce/catalog/sort-by-and-display-option>` "
"samt :ref:`snabbåtkomst till kategorier <ecommerce/catalog/categories>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:31
msgid "Sort-by search and display options"
msgstr "Sortera-efter sök- och visningsalternativ"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:33
msgid ""
"You can toggle the :guilabel:`Search Bar`, display :ref:`categories "
"<ecommerce/catalog/categories>` and/or :ref:`attributes <ecommerce/catalog/"
"attributes>`, and enable or disable the :guilabel:`Sort-By` as well as "
"the :ref:`Layout <ecommerce/catalog/layout>` buttons in the :guilabel:`Top "
"Bar`."
msgstr ""
"Du kan växla :guilabel:`Sökfält`, visa :ref:`kategorier <ecommerce/catalog/"
"categories>` och/eller :ref:`attribut <ecommerce/catalog/attributes>` samt "
"aktivera eller avaktivera knapparna :guilabel:`Sortera efter` och "
":ref:`Layout <ecommerce/catalog/layout>` i :guilabel:`Översta raden`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:38
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Sort-by` button is toggled by default, and customers can "
"choose between the following :guilabel:`Default Sort` options:"
msgstr ""
"Knappen :guilabel:`Sortera efter` är aktiverad som standard och kunder kan "
"välja mellan följande :guilabel:`Standardsortering`-alternativ:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:41
msgid ":guilabel:`None`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ingen`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:42
msgid ":guilabel:`Featured`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Utvald`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:43
msgid ":guilabel:`Newest Arrivals`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Nyaste ankomster`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:44
msgid ":guilabel:`Name (A-Z)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Namn (A-Ö)`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:45
msgid ":guilabel:`Price - Low to High`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Pris - lågt till högt`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:46
msgid ":guilabel:`Price - High to Low`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Pris - högt till lågt`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:48
msgid ""
"The default sort applies to *all* :ref:`categories <ecommerce/catalog/"
"categories>`."
msgstr ""
"Standardsorteringen gäller för *alla* :ref:`kategorier <ecommerce/catalog/"
"categories>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:51
msgid ""
"If you don't want to display a top bar or :ref:`side panel <ecommerce/"
"catalog/side-panel>`, you can disable all related options in the website "
"editor."
msgstr ""
"Om du inte vill visa en överrad eller ett :ref:`sidofält <ecommerce/catalog/"
"side-panel>`, kan du avaktivera alla relaterade optioner i hemsidans "
"redigerare."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:57
msgid "Side panel"
msgstr "Sidofält"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:59
msgid ""
"The side panel provides advanced filtering tools to organize your product "
"categories. To further :ref:`categorize <ecommerce/catalog/categories>` the "
"shop page, you can activate various filters, such as the :ref:`attribute "
"<ecommerce/catalog/attributes>` filter."
msgstr ""
"Sidofältet tillhandahåller avancerade filtreringsverktyg för att organisera "
"dina produktkategorier. För att ytterligare :ref:`kategorisera <ecommerce/"
"catalog/categories>` butikssidan kan du aktivera olika filter, såsom "
":ref:`attributfiltret <ecommerce/catalog/attributes>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:63
msgid ""
"You can also add a :guilabel:`Datepicker` option to display a date range "
"calendar to check the availability of rental products over a specific "
"period. The :doc:`Rental app <../../../sales/rental>` must be installed to "
"use this feature."
msgstr ""
"Du kan också lägga till ett :guilabel:`Datumväljare`-alternativ för att visa "
"en datumintervallkalender för att kryssa för tillgänglighet för "
"uthyrningsprodukter under en specifik period. :doc:`Uthyrningsappen <../../"
"../sales/rental>` måste vara installerad för att använda denna funktion."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:67
msgid ""
"It is also possible to toggle the :guilabel:`Collapsible sidebar` switch to "
"make the side panel manually collapsible."
msgstr ""
"Det är också möjligt att växla :guilabel:`Hopfällbar sidopanel`-reglaget för "
"att göra sidofältet manuellt hopfällbart."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:71
msgid ""
"To use a price range or tags filter, you have to enable :ref:`attributes "
"<ecommerce/catalog/attributes>` first."
msgstr ""
"För att använda ett prisintervallfilter eller taggfilter måste du aktivera "
":ref:`attribut <ecommerce/catalog/attributes>` först."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:77
msgid "Product categorization in catalog"
msgstr "Produktkategorisering i katalog"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:79
msgid ""
"eCommerce categories are used to organize products into groups, making it "
"easier for customers to browse the online store."
msgstr ""
"Webbshopskategorier används för att organisera produkter i grupper, vilket "
"gör det enklare för kunder attbläddra i onlinebutiken."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:82
msgid ""
"To create eCommerce categories, go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce "
"--> eCommerce Categories`, and click :guilabel:`New`. On the category form, "
"add a :guilabel:`Name`, optionally enter a :guilabel:`Parent Category`, and "
"write a :guilabel:`Category Description`, if needed."
msgstr ""
"För att skapa webbshopskategorier, gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> "
"Webbshop --> Webbshopskategorier`, och klicka på :guilabel:`Skapa`. På "
"kategoriformuläret, lägg till ett :guilabel:`Namn`, ange eventuellt en "
":guilabel:`Överordnad kategori`, och skriv en "
":guilabel:`Kategoribeskrivning`, om det behövs."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:87
msgid ""
"To use eCommerce categories, go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> "
"Products`, select the product you wish to modify, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, navigate to the :guilabel:`Ecommerce shop` "
"section, and select the :guilabel:`Categories` it belongs to."
msgstr ""
"För att använda webbshopskategorier, gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> "
"Webbshop --> Produkter`, välj den produkt du vill ändra, gå till fliken "
":guilabel:`Försäljning`, navigera till sektionen :guilabel:`Webbshopsbutik`, "
"och välj de :guilabel:`Kategorier` den tillhör."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:92
msgid "A single product can belong to multiple eCommerce categories."
msgstr "En enskild produkt kan tillhöra flera webbshopskategorier."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:94
msgid ""
"Once the categories are configured and assigned to the relevant products, go "
"to the main shop page and open the website editor. In "
"the :guilabel:`Categories` option, you can either enable a menu on "
"the :guilabel:`Left`, i.e., in the :ref:`side panel <ecommerce/catalog/side-"
"panel>`, or on the :guilabel:`Top`, i.e., in the :ref:`top bar <ecommerce/"
"catalog/top-bar>`, or both. If you select the :guilabel:`Left` category, the "
"option :guilabel:`Collapsible Category Recursive` appears, allowing you to "
"collapse the category in the side panel."
msgstr ""
"När kategorierna är konfigurerade och tilldelade till relevanta produkter, "
"gå till huvudbutikssidan och öppna hemsidans redigerare. I alternativet "
":guilabel:`Kategorier` kan du antingen aktivera en meny till "
":guilabel:`Vänster`, dvs. i :ref:`sidofältet <ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>"
"`, eller :guilabel:`Upptill`, dvs. i :ref:`överraden <ecommerce/catalog/top-"
"bar>`, eller båda. Om du väljer :guilabel:`Vänster`-kategorin visas "
"alternativet :guilabel:`Hopfällbar kategori rekursivt`, vilket gör det "
"möjligt att dölja kategorin i sidofältet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:None
msgid "Categories options for your eCommerce website"
msgstr "Alternativ för kategorier för din e-handelswebbplats"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:105
msgid ":doc:`../products`"
msgstr ":doc:`../produkter`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:110
msgid "Attributes"
msgstr "Attribut"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:112
msgid ""
"Attributes refer to characteristics of a product, such as the color or "
"material, whereas variants are the different combinations of attributes. To "
"configure attributes and variants, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Products`, select a product, and click "
"the :guilabel:`Attributes & Variants` tab. Add as many attributes as desired."
msgstr ""
"Attribut avser egenskaper hos en produkt, såsom färg eller material, medan "
"varianter är de olika kombinationerna av attribut. För att konfigurera "
"attribut och varianter, gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> Webbshop --> "
"Produkter`, välj en produkt och klicka på fliken :guilabel:`Attribut & "
"Varianter`. Lägg till så många attribut som önskas."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:118
msgid ":doc:`../../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:None
msgid "Attributes and variants of your product"
msgstr "Attribut och varianter av din produkt"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:123
msgid ""
"To enable attribute filtering, go to your main shop page, then open the "
"website editor, and set the :guilabel:`Attributes` field to :guilabel:`Left` "
"(:ref:`side panel <ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>`) and/or :guilabel:`Top` "
"(:ref:`top bar <ecommerce/catalog/top-bar>`)."
msgstr ""
"För att aktivera attributfiltrering, gå till din huvudbutikssida, öppna "
"sedan hemsidans redigerare och ställ in fältet :guilabel:`Attribut` till "
":guilabel:`Vänster` (:ref:`sidofält <ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>`) och/"
"eller :guilabel:`Upptill` (:ref:`överrad <ecommerce/catalog/top-bar>`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:129
msgid ""
"When attribute filtering is enabled in the top bar, customers must click "
"the :icon:`fa-sliders` (:guilabel:`dropdown toggle`) button to access it."
msgstr ""
"När attributfiltrering är aktiverad i överraden måste kunderna klicka på "
":icon:`fa-sliders` (:guilabel:`rullgardinsmenyväxling`)-knappen för att få "
"åtkomst till den."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:132
msgid "When enabling :guilabel:`Attributes`, more options become available:"
msgstr "När du aktiverar :guilabel:`Attribut` blir fler optioner tillgängliga:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:134
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Price Filter`: Toggle the switch to display a :guilabel:`Price "
"Range` bar, which allows customers to filter products according to a "
"specific price range by dragging adjustable handles."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Prisfilter`: Aktivera växeln för att visa en "
":guilabel:`Prisintervall`-stapel som gör det möjligt för kunder att filtrera "
"produkter enligt ett specifikt prisintervall genom att dra justerbara "
"handtag."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:137
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product Tags Filter`: Toggle the switch to display "
"the :guilabel:`Product Tags` on the shop page, and allow customers to filter "
"products using those tags by going to the :guilabel:`Tags` section in "
"the :ref:`side panel <ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Produkttaggfilter`: Växla reglaget för att visa "
":guilabel:`Produkttaggar` på butikssidan, och tillåta kunder att filtrera "
"produkter med dessa taggar genom att gå till sektionen :guilabel:`Taggar` i "
":ref:`sidofältet <ecommerce/catalog/side-panel>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:142
msgid ""
"If you want to use tags on your e-commerce, go to :menuselection:`eCommerce "
"--> Product Tags` and click :guilabel:`New`. In the :guilabel:`Product "
"Templates` tab of the product tags form, add the products to link to the "
"given tag. You can also add product variants in the :guilabel:`Product "
"Variants` tab and view a summary of all selected products in "
"the :guilabel:`All Products` tab."
msgstr ""
"Om du vill använda taggar på din webbshop, gå till "
":menuselection:`Webbshop --> Produkttaggar` och klicka på :guilabel:`Skapa`. "
"I fliken :guilabel:`Produktmallar` i produkttaggformuläret, lägg till de "
"produkter som ska länkas till den givna taggen. Du kan också lägga till "
"produktvarianter i fliken :guilabel:`Produktvarianter` och se en "
"sammanfattning av alla valda produkter i fliken :guilabel:`Alla produkter`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:147
msgid ""
"Price filtering works independently from attributes and, therefore, can be "
"enabled on its own, if desired."
msgstr ""
"Prisfiltrering fungerar oberoende från attribut och kan därför aktiveras på "
"egen hand, om så önskas."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:153
msgid "Product listing area"
msgstr "Produktlistningsområde"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:155
msgid ""
"You can customize the layout of the entire shop page, as well as that "
"of :ref:`individual category pages <ecommerce/catalog/customize-layout>`."
msgstr ""
"Du kan anpassa layouten för hela butikssidan, samt för :ref:`enskilda "
"kategorisidor <ecommerce/catalog/customize-layout>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:159
msgid ""
"It is also possible to customize individual :ref:`product pages <ecommerce/"
"products/product-form>`."
msgstr ""
"Det är också möjligt att anpassa enskilda :ref:`produktsidor <ecommerce/"
"products/product-form>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:163
msgid ""
"In the website editor, choose the :ref:`layout <ecommerce/catalog/sort-by-"
"and-display-option>`, and set the default layout to either :guilabel:`Grid` "
"or :guilabel:`List` view."
msgstr ""
"I hemsideredigeraren, välj :ref:`layouten <ecommerce/catalog/sort-by-and-"
"display-option>` och ställ in standardlayouten till antingen "
":guilabel:`Rutnät` eller :guilabel:`Lista`vy."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:166
msgid "Use the following options to further adjust the layout:"
msgstr "Använd följande optioner för att justera layouten ytterligare:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:168
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Size`: Set the number of products displayed per page and line."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Size`: Ställ in antalet produkter som visas per sida och rad."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:169
msgid ":guilabel:`Gap`: Define the gap between the products."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Mellanrum`: Definiera mellanrummet mellan produkterna."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:170
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Style`: "
"Select :guilabel:`Default`, :guilabel:`Cards`, :guilabel:`Thumbnails`, "
"or :guilabel:`Grid`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Stil`: Välj :guilabel:`Standard`, :guilabel:`Kort`, "
":guilabel:`Miniatyrbilder` eller :guilabel:`Rutnät`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:172
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Image Size`: Choose the aspect ratio for the product "
"images: :guilabel:`Landscape (4/3)`, :guilabel:`Default "
"(1/1)`, :guilabel:`Portrait (4/5)`, or :guilabel:`Vertical (2/3)`. You can "
"also adjust the display by changing the :guilabel:`Fill` options to fit your "
"design preferences best."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bildstorlek`: Välj bildförhållande för produktbilderna: "
":guilabel:`Liggande (4/3)`, :guilabel:`Standard (1/1)`, :guilabel:`Stående "
"(4/5)`, eller :guilabel:`Vertikal (2/3)`. Du kan också justera visningen "
"genom att ändra :guilabel:`Fyll`optionerna för att bäst passa dina "
"designpreferenser."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:177
msgid ""
"Toggle the :guilabel:`Prod. Desc.` switch to display the product description "
"below the product's name."
msgstr ""
"Växla :guilabel:`Prod. Besk.`bryteren för att visa produktbeskrivningen "
"under produktens namn."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:181
msgid ""
"You can choose the size of the grid, but be aware that displaying too many "
"products may affect performance and page loading speed."
msgstr ""
"Du kan välja storlek på rutnätet, men tänk på att om du visar för många "
"produkter kan det påverka prestandan och hastigheten när sidan laddas."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:184
msgid ""
"In addition, you can manually change a product’s position on the shop page. "
"To do so, go to the main shop page, click the product, and open the website "
"editor. In the :guilabel:`Product` section, you can reorder the products by "
"using the arrows. The `<<` `>>` buttons allow to move the product to the "
"extreme left or right, and `<` `>` allow to move it one row to the left or "
"right."
msgstr ""
"Dessutom kan du manuellt ändra en produkts position på butikssidan. För att "
"göra detta, gå till huvudbutikssidan, klicka på produkten och öppna "
"hemsideredigeraren. I :guilabel:`Produkt`sektionen kan du sortera "
"produkterna genom att använda pilarna. Knapparna `<<` `>>` låter dig flytta "
"produkten till yttersta vänster eller höger, och `<` `>` låter dig flytta "
"den en rad till vänster eller höger."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:190
msgid ""
"It is also possible to change the products' positions on the shop page by "
"going to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products`, switching to "
"the list view, and dragging and dropping the products within the list."
msgstr ""
"Det är också möjligt att ändra produkternas positioner på butikssidan genom "
"att gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> Webbshop --> Produkter`, växla till "
"listvyn och dra och släppa produkterna i listan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:195
msgid "Product highlight"
msgstr "Produktens höjdpunkt"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:197
msgid ""
"You can highlight products to make them more visible on the shop page. To do "
"so, go to the website editor and click the product to highlight. In "
"the :guilabel:`Product` section, you can choose the size of the product "
"image by clicking the grid, and you can also add a :guilabel:`Ribbon`. This "
"displays a banner across the product's image, such "
"as :guilabel:`Sale`, :guilabel:`Sold out`, :guilabel:`Out of stock` "
"or :guilabel:`New!`."
msgstr ""
"Du kan markera produkter för att göra dem mer synliga på butikssidan. För "
"att göra detta, gå till hemsideredigeraren och klicka på produkten du vill "
"markera. I :guilabel:`Produkt`sektionen kan du välja storleken på "
"produktbilden genom att klicka på rutnätet, och du kan också lägga till ett "
":guilabel:`Band`. Detta visar en banner över produktens bild, som "
":guilabel:`Rea`, :guilabel:`Slutsåld`, :guilabel:`Ej i lager` eller "
":guilabel:`Nyhet!`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:None
msgid "Ribbon highlight"
msgstr "Bandets höjdpunkt"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:206
msgid ""
"To create a new ribbon, click the green :icon:`fa-plus` (:guilabel:`Create`) "
"icon next to the :guilabel:`Ribbon` field. Then add a :guilabel:`Ribbon "
"name`, define its :guilabel:`Position`, and choose a :guilabel:`Background` "
"and a :guilabel:`Text` label. To edit the ribbon, click the :icon:`fa-pencil-"
"square-o` (:guilabel:`Edit`) icon next to the :guilabel:`Ribbon` label."
msgstr ""
"För att skapa ett nytt band, klicka på den gröna :icon:`fa-plus` "
"(:guilabel:`Skapa`) ikonen bredvid :guilabel:`Band`fältet. Lägg sedan till "
"ett :guilabel:`Bandnamn`, definiera dess :guilabel:`Position` och välj en "
":guilabel:`Bakgrund` och en :guilabel:`Text`etikett. För att redigera "
"bandet, klicka på :icon:`fa-pencil-square-o` (:guilabel:`Redigera`) ikonen "
"bredvid :guilabel:`Band`etiketten."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:None
msgid "Create a new ribbon."
msgstr "Skapa ett nytt band."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:214
msgid "The ribbon is now available for all the eCommerce products."
msgstr "Bandet är nu tillgängligt för alla webbshopprodukter."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:217
msgid "There are other ways to create a new ribbon:"
msgstr "Det finns andra sätt att skapa ett nytt band:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:219
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Product Ribbons` and "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> Webbshop --> Produktband` och klicka på "
":guilabel:`Skapa`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:220
msgid ""
"Activate the :doc:`developer mode <../../../general/developer_mode>`, access "
"the product form, and under the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, change or create the "
"ribbon in the :guilabel:`Ribbon` field."
msgstr ""
"Aktivera :doc:`systemutvecklarläget <../../../general/developer_mode>`, "
"öppna produktformuläret och under fliken :guilabel:`Försäljning`, ändra "
"eller skapa bandet i fältet :guilabel:`Band`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:224
msgid ""
"It is also possible to add ribbons for specific :ref:`product variants "
"<ecommerce/products/product-variants>`. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Products` and select a product. "
"Click the :guilabel:`Variants` smart button, choose a variant, and add a "
"ribbon in the :guilabel:`Variant Ribbon` field of the :guilabel:`Sales` "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Det är också möjligt att lägga till band för specifika "
":ref:`produktvarianter <ecommerce/products/product-variants>`. För att göra "
"detta, gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> Webbshop --> Produkter` och välj "
"en produkt. Klicka på den smarta knappen :guilabel:`Varianter`, välj en "
"variant och lägg till ett band i fältet :guilabel:`Variantband` i "
":guilabel:`Försäljning`sektionen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:233
msgid "Shop and category page design"
msgstr "Design av butiks- och kategorisidor"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:235
msgid ""
"Use :doc:`building blocks <../../website/web_design/building_blocks>` to add "
"content on the shop and/or category page."
msgstr ""
"Använd :doc:`byggmoduler <../../website/web_design/building_blocks>` för att "
"lägga till innehåll på butiks- och/eller kategorisidan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:238
msgid ""
"You can customize the top and/or bottom section of the catalog, either for "
"the entire shop page or for a specific category. In the latter case, the "
"block appears *only* when filtering by that category. To do so, move the "
"block to the far top or bottom section to display it on the general shop "
"page or to the area below the category's name at the top or beneath the "
"product list to display it only when filtering by that specific category."
msgstr ""
"Du kan anpassa den övre och/eller nedre sektionen av katalogen, antingen för "
"hela butikssidan eller för en specifik kategori. I det senare fallet visas "
"blocket *endast* vid filtrering efter den kategorin. För att göra detta, "
"flytta blocket till den översta eller understa sektionen för att visa det på "
"den generella butikssidan eller till området under kategorins namn högst upp "
"eller under produktlistan för att visa det endast vid filtrering efter den "
"specifika kategorin."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:0
msgid "Place building block in the header or footer."
msgstr "Placera byggmodulen i sidhuvudet eller sidfoten."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:248
msgid ""
"Adding content to an eCommerce category page helps improve the :doc:`SEO "
"<../../website/structure/seo>` strategy. Using keywords linked to the "
"products or the eCommerce categories can also increase organic traffic. "
"Additionally, each category has its own specific URL that can be pointed to "
"and is indexed by search engines."
msgstr ""
"Att lägga till innehåll på en webbshopskategorisida hjälper till att "
"förbättra :doc:`Sökmotoroptimering <../../website/structure/seo>`strategin. "
"Att använda nyckelord kopplade till produkterna eller webbshopskategorierna "
"kan också öka organisk trafik. Dessutom har varje kategori sin egen "
"specifika URL som kan pekas till och indexeras av sökmotorer."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:252
msgid ""
"eCommerce categories can also be added as :ref:`mega menu items <website/"
"header_footer/mega-menus>` for quick access."
msgstr ""
"Webbshopkategorier kan också läggas till som :ref:`megamenyalternativ "
"<website/header_footer/mega-menus>` för snabb åtkomst."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:260
msgid ""
"You can access and enable additional feature buttons such as "
"a :guilabel:`Add to cart` or :guilabel:`Wishlist` button or "
"a :guilabel:`Comparison list`. To do so, open the website editor, click the "
"desired feature buttons. All three buttons appear when hovering the mouse "
"over a product's image."
msgstr ""
"Du kan komma åt och aktivera ytterligare funktionsknappar såsom en "
":guilabel:`Lägg till i kundvagn` eller :guilabel:`Önskelista`knapp eller en "
":guilabel:`Jämförelselista`. För att göra detta, öppna hemsideredigeraren "
"och klicka på de önskade funktionsknapparna. Alla tre knapparna visas när du "
"håller muspekaren över en produkts bild."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:265
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-shopping-cart` (:guilabel:`Add to cart`): adds a button "
"to :doc:`add the product to the cart <../checkout>`;"
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-shopping-cart` (:guilabel:`Lägg till i kundvagn`): lägger till en "
"knapp för att :doc:`lägga till produkten i kundvagnen <../checkout>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:267
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Compare`): adds a button to compare products "
"based on their price, variant, etc.;"
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-exchange` (:guilabel:`Jämför`): lägger till en knapp för att "
"jämföra produkter baserat på pris, variant osv.;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:269
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-heart-o` (:guilabel:`Wishlist`): adds a button to :ref:`wishlist "
"<ecommerce/products/wishlists>` the product."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-heart-o` (:guilabel:`Önskelista`): lägger till en knapp för att "
":ref:`lägga produkten på önskelistan <ecommerce/products/wishlists>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/catalog.rst:274
msgid ":doc:`Products <../products>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Produkter <../products>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:3
msgid "Cross-selling and upselling"
msgstr "Korsförsäljning och merförsäljning"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:5
msgid ""
":ref:`Cross-selling <ecommerce/cross_selling>` and :ref:`upselling "
"<ecommerce/cross_upselling/alternative>` are sales techniques designed to "
"encourage customers to purchase additional or higher-priced products and "
"services from your :doc:`catalog`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Korsförsäljning <ecommerce/cross_selling>` och :ref:`merförsäljning "
"<ecommerce/cross_upselling/alternative>` är försäljningstekniker utformade "
"för att uppmuntra kunder att köpa ytterligare eller dyrare produkter och "
"tjänster från din :doc:`catalog`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:12
msgid "Cross-selling"
msgstr "Korsförsäljning"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:14
msgid ""
"Cross-selling can be achieved by suggesting :ref:`optional products "
"<ecommerce/cross_upselling/optional>` when items are added to the cart or by "
"recommending :ref:`accessory products <ecommerce/cross_upselling/accessory>` "
"on the checkout page."
msgstr ""
"Korsförsäljning kan uppnås genom att föreslå :ref:`valfria produkter "
"<ecommerce/cross_upselling/optional>` när artiklar läggs till i kundvagnen "
"eller genom att rekommendera :ref:`tillbehörsprodukter <ecommerce/"
"cross_upselling/accessory>` på kassasidan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:21
msgid "Optional products"
msgstr "Valfria produkter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:23
msgid ""
"**Optional products** are suggested when the customer selects a product and "
"clicks :guilabel:`Add to cart`."
msgstr ""
"**Valfria produkter** föreslås när kunden väljer en produkt och klickar på "
":guilabel:`Lägg till i kundvagn`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:26
msgid ""
"To enable **optional products**, go to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce "
"--> Products`, select a product, go to the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, and enter "
"the products you wish to feature in the :guilabel:`Optional Products` field."
msgstr ""
"För att aktivera **valfria produkter**, gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> "
"Webbshop --> Produkter`, välj en produkt, gå till fliken "
":guilabel:`Försäljning`, och ange de produkter du vill visa i fältet "
":guilabel:`Valfria produkter`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:None
msgid "Optional products cross-selling"
msgstr "Korsförsäljning av valfria produkter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:36
msgid "Accessory products"
msgstr "Tillbehörsprodukter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:38
msgid ""
"**Accessory products** are showcased in the :guilabel:`Suggested "
"Accessories` section during the :guilabel:`Review Order` step, just before "
"proceeding to checkout."
msgstr ""
"**Tillbehörsprodukter** visas i sektionen :guilabel:`Föreslagna tillbehör` "
"under steget :guilabel:`Granska beställning`, precis innan man går vidare "
"till kassan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:41
msgid ""
"To enable **accessory products**, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Products`, select a product, go to the :guilabel:`Sales` tab, "
"and enter the products you wish to feature in the :guilabel:`Accessory "
"Products` field."
msgstr ""
"För att aktivera **tillbehörsprodukter**, gå till "
":menuselection:`Hemsida --> Webbshop --> Produkter`, välj en produkt, gå "
"till fliken :guilabel:`Försäljning`, och ange de produkter du vill visa i "
"fältet :guilabel:`Tillbehörsprodukter`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:None
msgid "Suggested accessories at checkout during cart review"
msgstr "Föreslagna tillbehör i kassan under granskning av varukorgen"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:51
msgid "Upselling"
msgstr "Merförsäljning"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:53
msgid ""
"You can display **alternative products** at the bottom of the product page "
"as an upselling technique, encouraging customers to consider a more "
"expensive variant or product than their initial choice by presenting "
"appealing alternatives."
msgstr ""
"Du kan visa **alternativa produkter** längst ned på produktsidan som en "
"merförsäljningsteknik, vilket uppmuntrar kunder att överväga en dyrare "
"variant eller produkt än deras ursprungliga val genom att presentera "
"tilltalande alternativ."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:None
msgid "Alternative products on the product page"
msgstr "Alternativa produkter på produktsidan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:60
msgid ""
"To enable alternative products, navigate to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Products`, select the desired product, and go to "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` tab. In the :guilabel:`Alternative Products` field, "
"add the products you want to feature."
msgstr ""
"För att aktivera alternativa produkter, navigera till "
":menuselection:`Hemsida --> Webbshop --> Produkter`, välj önskad produkt och "
"gå till fliken :guilabel:`Försäljning`. I fältet :guilabel:`Alternativa "
"produkter`, lägg till de produkter du vill visa."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:64
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Go to Website` to view the alternative products displayed "
"at the bottom of the product page."
msgstr ""
"Klicka på :guilabel:`Gå till hemsida` för att visa de alternativa "
"produkterna som visas längst ned på produktsidan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling.rst:67
msgid ""
"To adjust the settings, click :guilabel:`Edit` and select the "
"related :doc:`building block <../../website/web_design/building_blocks>`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Customize` tab, scroll to the :guilabel:`Alternative "
"Products` section and modify the settings as needed to tailor the display to "
"your preferences."
msgstr ""
"För att justera inställningarna, klicka på :guilabel:`Redigera` och välj "
"relaterad :doc:`byggmodul <../../website/web_design/building_blocks>`. I "
"fliken :guilabel:`Anpassa`, rulla till sektionen :guilabel:`Alternativa "
"produkter` och ändra inställningarna efter behov för att anpassa visningen "
"enligt dina preferenser."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo offers multiple options to configure prices on the ecommerce. For "
"example, you can apply :ref:`prices per unit <ecommerce/prices/price-per-"
"unit>`, offer :ref:`discounts <ecommerce/prices/discounts>`, and set "
"up :ref:`pricelists <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo erbjuder flera alternativ för att konfigurera priser på webbshopen. "
"Till exempel kan du tillämpa :ref:`priser per enhet <ecommerce/prices/price-"
"per-unit>`, erbjuda :ref:`rabatter <ecommerce/prices/discounts>` och ställa "
"in :ref:`prislistor <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:12
msgid "Taxes"
msgstr "Skatter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:14
msgid ""
"To add a tax on a product, you can either set a tax in "
"the :guilabel:`Customer Taxes` field of the **product template** or "
"use :doc:`fiscal positions </applications/finance/accounting/taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>`."
msgstr ""
"För att lägga till en skatt på en produkt kan du antingen ange en skatt i "
"fältet :guilabel:`Customer Taxes` i **produktmallen** eller "
"använda :doc:`fiscal positions </applications/finance/accounting/taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:19
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/taxes`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/taxes`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:20
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:24
msgid ""
"Choosing the displayed price tax usually depends on a country's regulations "
"or the type of customers (:doc:`B2B vs. B2C <../b2b_b2c>`). To select the "
"type of price displayed, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, select the website, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Shop - "
"Products` section, and under :guilabel:`Display Product Prices` select "
"between:"
msgstr ""
"Valet av visat pris med moms beror vanligtvis på ett lands regler eller "
"typen av kunder (:doc:`B2B vs. B2C <../b2b_b2c>`). För att välja vilken typ "
"av pris som visas, gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> Konfiguration --> "
"Inställningar`, välj hemsidan, scrolla ner till sektionen :guilabel:`Butik - "
"Produkter`, och under :guilabel:`Visa produktpriser` välj mellan:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:29
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tax Excluded`: the price displayed on the website is tax-"
"excluded, and the tax is computed at the :ref:`order review <ecommerce/"
"checkout/review_order>` step;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Moms exklusive`: priset som visas på webbplatsen är exklusive "
"moms, och momsen beräknas i steget :ref:`granska beställning <ecommerce/"
"checkout/review_order>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:31
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tax Included`: the price displayed on the website is tax-included."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Inklusive skatt`: priset som visas på hemsidan är inklusive skatt."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:34
msgid ""
"This setting is website-specific and can therefore be configured "
"independently for every website in the database."
msgstr ""
"Denna inställning är hemsidspecifik och kan därför konfigureras oberoende "
"för varje hemsida i databasen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:38
msgid ""
"Switch the :ref:`Tax indication <ecommerce/products/product-presentation>` "
"toggle on in the website editor to explicitly indicate if the price is `Tax "
"excluded` or `Tax included` on the product page."
msgstr ""
"Slå på växlingsknappen :ref:`Momsindikering <ecommerce/products/product-"
"presentation>` i webbplatsredigeraren för att uttryckligen ange om priset är "
"`Moms exklusive` eller `Moms inklusive` på produktsidan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:41
msgid ""
"Enable specific :ref:`B2B fields <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/b2b-fields>` in "
"the :ref:`delivery step <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>` during the checkout "
"using the :doc:`website editor </applications/websites/website/web_design>`."
msgstr ""
"Aktivera specifika :ref:`B2B-fält <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/b2b-fields>` i "
":ref:`leveranssteget <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>` under kassan med hjälp "
"av :doc:`hemsidans redigerare </applications/websites/website/web_design>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:48
msgid "Price per unit"
msgstr "Pris per enhet"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:50
msgid ""
"To display a :doc:`price per unit </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"product_management/configure/uom>` alongside the sales price on the product "
"page, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"För att visa ett :doc:`pris per enhet </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/product_management/configure/uom>` tillsammans med "
"försäljningspriset på produktsidan, följ dessa steg:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:54
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll to "
"the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section, and enable :guilabel:`Product "
"Reference Price`."
msgstr ""
"Gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> Konfiguration --> Inställningar`, rulla "
"ner till avsnittet :guilabel:`Butik - Produkter` och aktivera "
":guilabel:`Produktjämförelsepris`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:56
msgid ""
":ref:`Navigate to the product form <ecommerce/products/create-products>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Navigera till produktformuläret <ecommerce/products/create-products>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:57
msgid ""
"Set the product's :guilabel:`Sales price` and select the unit "
"(e.g., :guilabel:`Units`)."
msgstr ""
"Ange produktens :guilabel:`försäljningspris` och välj enheten (t.ex. "
":guilabel:`Enheter`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:58
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Base Unit Count` field, enter the number of units in the "
"product, then select the relevant unit from the dropdown list."
msgstr ""
"I fältet :guilabel:`Antal basenheter`, ange antalet enheter i produkten och "
"välj sedan relevant enhet från rullgardinsmenyn."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:62
msgid ""
"Imagine you want to sell a 2-liter bucket of paint for $60, i.e., $30 per "
"liter."
msgstr ""
"Föreställ dig att du vill sälja en 2-liters färghink för 60 $, dvs. 30 $ per "
"liter."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:0
msgid "Cost per unit pricing on the product form."
msgstr "Kostnad per enhet på produktformuläret."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:67
msgid ""
"The price per units, in this case per liter, is shown next to the sales "
"price on the product page."
msgstr ""
"Priset per enhet, i detta fall per liter, visas bredvid försäljningspriset "
"på produktsidan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:0
msgid "Unit pricing on the product page."
msgstr "Enhetsprissättning på produktsidan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:74
msgid "The price per unit may be mandatory in some countries."
msgstr "Priset per enhet kan vara obligatoriskt i vissa länder."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:77
msgid ""
":doc:`/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/"
"uom`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/"
"uom`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:82
msgid "Pricelists"
msgstr "Prislistor"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:84
msgid ""
"Pricelists in Odoo allow to manage flexible pricing rules and to offer "
"different prices and discounts based on currencies, time periods, purchase "
"volumes, :ref:`customers' location <ecommerce/prices/geoip>`, and/or "
"customer type. To enable pricelists for eCommerce, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section, enable :guilabel:`Pricelists`, "
"and :guilabel:`Save`. Then, click :guilabel:`Pricelists` or go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Pricelists` and :ref:`configure "
"<sales/products/pricelist-configuration>` the relevant pricelists."
msgstr ""
"Prislistor i Odoo möjliggör hantering av flexibla prisregler och att erbjuda "
"olika priser och rabatter baserat på valutor, tidsperioder, inköpsvolymer, "
":ref:`kundens plats <ecommerce/prices/geoip>` och/eller kundtyp. För att "
"aktivera prislistor för webbshop, gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> "
"Konfiguration --> Inställningar`, rulla ner till avsnittet "
":guilabel:`Butik - Produkter`, aktivera :guilabel:`Prislistor` och "
":guilabel:`Spara`. Klicka sedan på :guilabel:`Prislistor` eller gå till "
":menuselection:`Hemsida --> Webbshop --> Prislistor` och :ref:`konfigurera "
"<sales/products/pricelist-configuration>` relevanta prislistor."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:93
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Ecommerce` tab, configure options specific to online "
"sales, such as assigning a :guilabel:`Website` to a pricelist, allowing "
"customers to :ref:`select it <ecommerce/prices/selectable-pricelists>`, and/"
"or adding an :ref:`E-commerce Promotional Code <ecommerce/prices/promotional-"
"code>`."
msgstr ""
"I fliken :guilabel:`Webbshop`, konfigurera alternativ specifika för "
"onlineförsäljning, såsom att tilldela en :guilabel:`Hemsida` till en "
"prislista, tillåta kunder att :ref:`välja den <ecommerce/prices/selectable-"
"pricelists>` och/eller lägga till en :ref:`kampanjkod för webbshop "
"<ecommerce/prices/promotional-code>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:99
msgid ""
"If you are using several websites and you want to use the same pricelist on "
"several of them, you need to duplicate the pricelist for each website. If "
"you do not assign any website, the pricelist will not be used, unless it "
"is :ref:`selectable <ecommerce/prices/selectable-pricelists>`."
msgstr ""
"Om du använder flera hemsidor och vill använda samma prislista på flera av "
"dem, behöver du skapa en kopia av prislistan för varje hemsida. Om du inte "
"tilldelar någon hemsida kommer prislistan inte att användas, såvida den inte "
"är :ref:`valbar <ecommerce/prices/selectable-pricelists>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:103
msgid ""
"Pricelists can also be :ref:`assigned to a specific customer <sales/products/"
"customer-pricelist-application>`."
msgstr ""
"Prislistor kan också :ref:`tilldelas en specifik kund <sales/products/"
"customer-pricelist-application>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:107
msgid ""
"When pricelists are enabled in the Sales app, they are automatically enabled "
"in the eCommerce app, and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"När prislistor är aktiverade i appen Försäljning aktiveras de automatiskt i "
"appen Webbshop, och vice versa."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:109
msgid ""
"In the list of pricelists, order the pricelists by priority: the first takes "
"precedence over the second, the second over the third, and so on."
msgstr ""
"I listan över prislistor, sortera prislistorna efter prioritet: den första "
"har företräde framför den andra, den andra framför den tredje och så vidare."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:111
msgid ""
"It is also possible to create specific pricelists for :ref:`variants "
"<products/variants/configure-variants>`."
msgstr ""
"Det är också möjligt att skapa specifika prislistor för :ref:`varianter "
"<products/variants/configure-variants>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:115
msgid ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:120
msgid "Selectable pricelists"
msgstr "Valbara prislistor"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:122
msgid ""
"Selectable pricelists are useful, for example, when selling products "
"in :doc:`multiple currencies </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/"
"prices/currencies>` and allow customers to choose a pricelist using the "
"catalog's pricelist selector located next to the :ref:`search bar <ecommerce/"
"catalog/top-bar>`."
msgstr ""
"Valbara prislistor är användbara, till exempel, när man säljer produkter i "
":doc:`flera valutor </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/prices/"
"currencies>` och tillåter kunder att välja en prislista med hjälp av "
"katalogens prislistaväljare som finns bredvid :ref:`sökfältet <ecommerce/"
"catalog/top-bar>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:None
msgid "Pricelist selector on the ecommerce."
msgstr "Prislistaväljare på webbshopen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:130
msgid "To make a pricelist selectable, enable :guilabel:`Selectable`."
msgstr "För att göra en prislista valbar, aktivera :guilabel:`Valbar`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:133
msgid ""
"If a pricelist is designated as :guilabel:`Selectable`, and is not assigned "
"to a specific website, then the pricelist is selectable on **all** websites."
msgstr ""
"Om en prislista är markerad som :guilabel:`Valbar` och inte är tilldelad en "
"specifik hemsida, är prislistan valbar på **alla** hemsidor."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:135
msgid ""
"If a pricelist does *not* appear in the selector, it may be due to the "
"following situations:"
msgstr ""
"Om en prislista *inte* visas i väljaren kan det bero på följande situationer:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:137
msgid ""
"Only one pricelist is defined as :guilabel:`Selectable` and "
"the :ref:`contact has a pricelist assigned <sales/products/customer-"
"pricelist-application>`."
msgstr ""
"Endast en prislista är definierad som :guilabel:`Valbar` och :ref:`kontakten "
"har en prislista tilldelad <sales/products/customer-pricelist-application>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:139
msgid ""
"Multiple selectable pricelists exist, but only those matching the "
"customer's :ref:`country group <ecommerce/prices/country-groups>` are shown. "
"It is strongly recommended to disable the :guilabel:`Selectable` option when "
"using pricelists with country groups on the ecommerce."
msgstr ""
"Flera valbara prislistor finns, men endast de som matchar kundens "
":ref:`landgrupp <ecommerce/prices/country-groups>` visas. Det rekommenderas "
"starkt att inaktivera alternativet :guilabel:`Valbar` när du använder "
"prislistor med landgrupper på webbshopen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:145
msgid ":ref:`sales/products/currencies/currency-specific-pricelists`"
msgstr ":ref:`sales/products/currencies/currency-specific-pricelists`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:150
msgid "GeoIP & country groups"
msgstr "GeoIP & landsgrupper"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:152
msgid ""
"It is possible to display a specific pricelist based on the visitor's "
"location and IP address by assigning :ref:`country groups <ecommerce/prices/"
"country-groups>` to pricelists."
msgstr ""
"Det är möjligt att visa en specifik prislista baserat på besökarens plats "
"och IP-adress genom att tilldela :ref:`landsgrupper <ecommerce/prices/"
"country-groups>` till prislistor."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:157
msgid ""
"To do so, :ref:`navigate to the relevant pricelist form <ecommerce/prices/"
"pricelists>` and select the appropriate :guilabel:`Country Groups`. Create "
"or edit as many pricelists for specific regions as needed. For instance, "
"select :guilabel:`European Union` to apply the pricelist to all EU member "
"states."
msgstr ""
"För att göra detta, :ref:`navigera till relevant prislista <ecommerce/prices/"
"pricelists>` och välj lämpliga :guilabel:`Landsgrupper`. Skapa eller "
"redigera så många prislistor för specifika regioner som behövs. Till "
"exempel, välj :guilabel:`Europeiska unionen` för att tillämpa prislistan på "
"alla EU-medlemsstater."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:162
msgid ""
"To create a new country group, click :guilabel:`Search more` in the dropdown "
"list, then :guilabel:`New`. Add a :guilabel:`Group Name` and select the "
"relevant :guilabel:`Countries`. Use :ref:`Custom filters <search/custom-"
"filters>` if needed."
msgstr ""
"För att skapa en ny landsgrupp, klicka på :guilabel:`Sök mer` i "
"rullgardinsmenyn, sedan :guilabel:`Ny`. Lägg till ett :guilabel:`Gruppnamn` "
"och välj relevanta :guilabel:`Länder`. Använd :ref:`anpassade filter <search/"
"custom-filters>` om det behövs."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:167
msgid "Each country group must contain at least one country."
msgstr "Varje landsgrupp måste innehålla åtminstone ett land."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:170
msgid ""
"Use the following filter if you want to add all non-EU countries to the "
"country group."
msgstr ""
"Använd följande filter om du vill lägga till alla länder utanför EU i "
"landgruppen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:172
msgid "`Country Group` + `is not in` + `European Union`"
msgstr "`Landgrupp` + `är inte i` + `Europeiska unionen`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:0
msgid "Filter for country group creation."
msgstr "Filter för skapande av landgrupp."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:178
msgid ""
"When using GeoIP to determine the appropriate pricelist, **all** pricelists "
"used on the ecommerce must have a country group assigned."
msgstr ""
"När du använder GeoIP för att bestämma lämplig prislista måste **alla** "
"prislistor som används på webbshopen ha en tilldelad landgrupp."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:180
msgid ""
"It is strongly recommended to disable the :guilabel:`Selectable` option when "
"using pricelists with country groups. Indeed, all pricelists with the "
"relevant country group are automatically applied to the catalog but if one "
"of them is marked as :ref:`Selectable <ecommerce/prices/selectable-"
"pricelists>`, the others will disappear as soon as customers select the "
"selectable pricelist."
msgstr ""
"Det rekommenderas starkt att avaktivera alternativet :guilabel:`Selectable` "
"när du använder prislistor med landgrupper. Alla prislistor med relevant "
"landgrupp tillämpas automatiskt på katalogen, men om en av dem är markerad "
"som :ref:`Selectable <ecommerce/prices/selectable-pricelists>` kommer de "
"andra att försvinna så snart kunder väljer den valbara prislistan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:187
msgid "Imagine you create three pricelists:"
msgstr "Föreställ dig att du skapar tre prislistor:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:189
msgid "`EU regular prices` with the `EU` country group assigned"
msgstr "`EU regular prices` med landgruppen `EU` tilldelad"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:190
msgid "`EU prices with discounts` with the `EU` country group assigned"
msgstr "`EU prices with discounts` med landgruppen `EU` tilldelad"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:191
msgid "`US prices` with the `US` country group assigned"
msgstr "`US prices` med landgruppen `US` tilldelad"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:193
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Selectable` option is enabled for `EU regular prices` and "
"`US prices`, and the customer is from the European Union, only the "
"pricelists `EU regular prices` and `EU prices with discounts` will be "
"available. However, since the `EU prices with discount` list is not "
"selectable, it will disappear once the customer selects the `EU regular "
"prices` list and prices will be displayed based on the `EU regular prices` "
"pricelist on the catalog."
msgstr ""
"Om alternativet :guilabel:`Selectable` är aktiverat för `EU regular prices` "
"och `US prices`, och kunden kommer från Europeiska unionen, kommer endast "
"prislistorna `EU regular prices` och `EU prices with discounts` att vara "
"tillgängliga. Men eftersom listan `EU prices with discount` inte är valbar "
"kommer den att försvinna när kunden väljer listan `EU regular prices` och "
"priser kommer att visas baserat på prislistan `EU regular prices` i "
"katalogen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:201
msgid "Pricelist application"
msgstr "Tillämpning av prislista"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:203
msgid ""
"On the ecommerce, the *default* pricelist is automatically selected for "
"public, non-logged in users when no country group is assigned. "
"If :ref:`GeoIP and country groups <ecommerce/prices/geoip>` are used, public "
"users see the pricelist of their country group by default. Logged-in users "
"with :ref:`assigned pricelists <sales/products/customer-pricelist-"
"application>` see the assigned pricelist by default **if it is assigned to "
"the website** they are visiting. If not, the website's default pricelist is "
"applied (i.e., the first available pricelist assigned to the website and "
"without a country group, following the sequence order)."
msgstr ""
"På webbshopen väljs *standardprisisten* automatiskt för offentliga, icke-"
"inloggade användare när ingen landgrupp är tilldelad. Om :ref:`GeoIP och "
"landgrupper <ecommerce/prices/geoip>` används, ser offentliga användare "
"prislistan för sin landgrupp som standard. Inloggade användare med "
":ref:`tilldelade prislistor <sales/products/customer-pricelist-application>` "
"ser den tilldelade prislistan som standard **om den är tilldelad "
"webbplatsen** de besöker. Om inte, tillämpas webbplatsens standardprislista "
"(dvs. den första tillgängliga prislistan som är tilldelad webbplatsen och "
"utan landgrupp, enligt nummerserieordning)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:211
msgid ""
"Assigned pricelists take precedence over country-based pricelists, when "
"applicable, unless the assigned pricelist is linked to a different country "
"group."
msgstr ""
"Tilldelade prislistor har företräde framför landsbaserade prislistor, när "
"det är tillämpligt, såvida inte den tilldelade prislistan är kopplad till en "
"annan landgrupp."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:215
msgid ""
"A customer from the United States visits the website. They do not have a "
"portal account. The :guilabel:`United States` pricelist is applied."
msgstr ""
"En kund från USA besöker hemsidan. De har inget portalkonto. Prislistan "
":guilabel:`USA` tillämpas."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:218
msgid ""
"A different visitor, also from the United States, has the :guilabel:`Loyal "
"Customer Discount` pricelist assigned in their contact form. This assignment "
"takes precedence over the country group assignation, so the :guilabel:`Loyal "
"Customer Discount` is applied."
msgstr ""
"En annan besökare, också från USA, har prislistan :guilabel:`Loyal Customer "
"Discount` tilldelad i sitt kontaktformulär. Denna tilldelning har företräde "
"framför landgruppstilldelningen, så :guilabel:`Loyal Customer Discount` "
"tillämpas."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:0
msgid "An example of various pricelists assigned to a website."
msgstr "Ett exempel på olika prislistor tilldelade en hemsida."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:229
msgid "Discounts"
msgstr "Rabatter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:232
msgid "Discounts programs"
msgstr "Rabattprogram"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:234
msgid ""
"To enable :doc:`discount programs </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/"
"loyalty_discount>` for your ecommerce, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` "
"section, and enable the :guilabel:`Discounts, Loyalty & Gift Card` feature."
msgstr ""
"För att aktivera :doc:`rabattprogram </applications/sales/sales/"
"products_prices/loyalty_discount>` för din webbshop, gå till "
":menuselection:`Hemsida --> Konfiguration --> Inställningar`, rulla ner till "
"avsnittet :guilabel:`Butik - Produkter` och aktivera funktionen "
":guilabel:`Rabatter, lojalitet & presentkort`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:239
msgid ""
":ref:`Configure <sales/products/loyalty-programs>` the discount program, "
"make sure the :guilabel:`Website` option is enabled, and add the "
"relevant :ref:`Pricelist <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` "
"and :guilabel:`Website` on the program form, if needed."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Konfigurera <sales/products/loyalty-programs>` rabattprogrammet, se "
"till att alternativet :guilabel:`Website` är aktiverat och lägg till "
"relevant :ref:`Pricelist <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` och "
":guilabel:`Website` på programformuläret vid behov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:246
msgid "Permanent product discount"
msgstr "Permanent produktrabatt"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:248
msgid ""
"If the price of a specific product has been permanently reduced, the "
"strikethrough strategy is commonly used. This involves showing the new "
"discounted price, with the original price crossed out alongside it."
msgstr ""
"Om priset på en specifik produkt har sänkts permanent används vanligtvis "
"genomstrykningsstrategin. Detta innebär att man visar det nya rabatterade "
"priset med det ursprungliga priset överstruket bredvid."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:None
msgid "Price strikethrough."
msgstr "Överstruken prissättning."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:255
msgid ""
"To display a permanently discounted price, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`Shop - Products`, enable the :guilabel:`Comparison Price` "
"option, and :guilabel:`Save`. Then, :ref:`go to the product form <ecommerce/"
"products/create-products>`, enter the new (discounted) price in "
"the :guilabel:`Sales Price` field and the original one (strikethrough) in "
"the :guilabel:`Compare to Price` field."
msgstr ""
"För att visa ett permanent rabatterat pris, navigera till "
":menuselection:`Hemsida --> Konfiguration --> Inställningar`, rulla ner till "
":guilabel:`Butik - Produkter`, aktivera alternativet "
":guilabel:`Jämförelsepris` och :guilabel:`Spara`. Sedan, :ref:`gå till "
"produktformuläret <ecommerce/products/create-products>`, ange det nya "
"(rabatterade) priset i fältet :guilabel:`Försäljningspris` och det "
"ursprungliga (överstruket) i fältet :guilabel:`Jämför med pris`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:263
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Compare to Price` field must contain a price that is higher "
"than the :guilabel:`Sales Price` for the original price to appear with a "
"strikethrough."
msgstr ""
"Fältet :guilabel:`Compare to Price` måste innehålla ett pris som är högre än "
":guilabel:`Sales Price` för att det ursprungliga priset ska visas med en "
"genomstrykning."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:267
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Compare to Price` is not displayed if discounted pricelists "
"apply. If you want to use the :guilabel:`Compare to price` with another "
"discount, configure a pricelist with a :ref:`promotional code <ecommerce/"
"prices/promotional-code>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Compare to Price` visas inte om rabatterade prislistor tillämpas. "
"Om du vill använda :guilabel:`Compare to price` med en annan rabatt, "
"konfigurera en prislista med en :ref:`promotional code <ecommerce/prices/"
"promotional-code>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:272
msgid "Discounted pricelists"
msgstr "Rabatterade prislistor"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:274
msgid ""
"It is also possible to create :ref:`pricelists with discounts <sales/"
"products/price-rules>`. To do so, :ref:`create a pricelist <sales/products/"
"pricelist-configuration>` and :ref:`configure the discount <sales/products/"
"price-rules>`."
msgstr ""
"Det är också möjligt att skapa :ref:`pricelists with discounts <sales/"
"products/price-rules>`. För att göra detta, :ref:`create a pricelist <sales/"
"products/pricelist-configuration>` och :ref:`configure the discount <sales/"
"products/price-rules>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:278
msgid ""
"If a :ref:`pricelist <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` contains "
"a :ref:`Discount <sales/products/price-rules>` price type, the price is "
"striked through for applicable customers, even if the :ref:`Comparison Price "
"<ecommerce/prices/permanent-discounts>` feature has not been enabled."
msgstr ""
"Om en :ref:`prislista <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` innehåller en "
":ref:`Rabatt <sales/products/price-rules>` pristyp, är priset överstruket "
"för tillämpliga kunder, även om funktionen :ref:`Jämförelsepris <ecommerce/"
"prices/permanent-discounts>` inte har aktiverats."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:284
msgid ""
"If using pricelists with :ref:`country groups <ecommerce/prices/geoip>`, the "
"discounted pricelist must be assigned the same country group as the one used "
"for the non-discounted pricelist."
msgstr ""
"Om du använder prislistor med :ref:`landsgrupper <ecommerce/prices/geoip>`, "
"måste den rabatterade prislistan tilldelas samma landsgrupp som den som "
"används för den icke-rabatterade prislistan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:290
msgid "E-commerce promotional code"
msgstr "Kampanjkod för webbshop"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:292
msgid ""
"To offer a discounted pricelist for customers with a specific discount code, "
"access the relevant :ref:`pricelist form <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>`, go "
"to the :guilabel:`Ecommerce` tab, and add an :guilabel:`E-commerce "
"Promotional Code`, e.g., `SUMMERSALE10%`. Then, go to the :guilabel:`Price "
"Rules` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a line`, and :ref:`configure the discount "
"<sales/products/price-rules>`. When a customer inserts the code during "
"the :ref:`checkout process <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>`, this discount "
"is granted according to the :guilabel:`Price Rules` configuration."
msgstr ""
"För att erbjuda en rabatterad prislista för kunder med en specifik "
"rabattkod, gå till relevant :ref:`prislistaformulär <ecommerce/prices/"
"pricelists>`, gå till fliken :guilabel:`Webbshop` och lägg till en "
":guilabel:`Webbshop-kampanjkod`, t.ex. `SUMMERSALE10%`. Gå sedan till fliken "
":guilabel:`Prisregler`, klicka på :guilabel:`Lägg till en rad` och "
":ref:`konfigurera rabatten <sales/products/price-rules>`. När en kund anger "
"koden under :ref:`utcheckningsprocessen <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>`, "
"beviljas denna rabatt enligt konfigurationen för :guilabel:`Prisregler`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:301
msgid ""
"Make sure that the :ref:`Promo Code <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>` "
"option in the website editor is enabled and, if using :ref:`country groups "
"<ecommerce/prices/country-groups>`, that the discounted pricelist has the "
"same country group assigned as the non-discounted pricelist."
msgstr ""
"Se till att alternativet :ref:`Kampanjkod <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>` "
"i hemsidans redigerare är aktiverat och, om du använder :ref:`landsgrupper "
"<ecommerce/prices/country-groups>`, att den rabatterade prislistan har samma "
"landsgrupp tilldelad som den icke-rabatterade prislistan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:309
msgid "Hide prices"
msgstr "Dölj priser"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:311
msgid ""
"Some businesses, such as :ref:`B2B shops <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/prices>` or "
"companies that sell luxury or custom items, often prefer to showcase their "
"products online without displaying their prices."
msgstr ""
"Vissa företag, såsom :ref:`B2B-butiker <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/prices>` eller "
"företag som säljer lyxvaror eller skräddarsydda artiklar, föredrar ofta att "
"visa sina produkter online utan att visa priserna."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:314
msgid ""
"To hide product prices on the ecommerce, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, enable :guilabel:`Prevent Sale of Zero Priced "
"Product` in the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section, and enter a redirect "
"URL in the :guilabel:`Button URL` field. The :guilabel:`Add to Cart` button "
"on the product page is then replaced by a :guilabel:`Contact us` button, "
"which can be :ref:`customized <ecommerce/checkout/prevent-sale>` if needed."
msgstr ""
"Pro skrytí cen produktů na webu přejděte na :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, aktivujte :guilabel:`Prevent Sale of Zero "
"Priced Product` v sekci :guilabel:`Shop - Products` a zadejte URL "
"přesměrování do pole :guilabel:`Button URL`. Tlačítko :guilabel:`Add to "
"Cart` na stránce produktu bude pak nahrazeno tlačítkem :guilabel:`Contact "
"us`, které lze v případě potřeby :ref:`přizpůsobit <ecommerce/checkout/"
"prevent-sale>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:320
msgid ""
"After enabling this feature, either set the price to `0` for all desired "
"products or create a :ref:`pricelist <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` with all "
"product prices set to `0`. Ensure the pricelist is assigned to the correct "
"website and is listed first among the website's pricelists."
msgstr ""
"Efter att ha aktiverat denna funktion, sätt antingen priset till `0` för "
"alla önskade produkter eller skapa en :ref:`prislista <ecommerce/prices/"
"pricelists>` med alla produktpriser satta till `0`. Se till att prislistan "
"är tilldelad rätt hemsida och är listad först bland hemsidans prislistor."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:325
msgid ""
"Ensure no pricelist used on the ecommerce has been marked "
"as :guilabel:`Selectable` to prevent accidentally displaying the zero-priced "
"pricelist."
msgstr ""
"Ujistěte se, že žádný ceník používaný na webu není označen jako "
":guilabel:`Selectable`, abyste zabránili náhodnému zobrazení ceníku s "
"nulovou cenou."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:327
msgid ""
"To hide prices from public visitors while keeping them visible to logged-in "
"customers, create a zero-priced pricelist to be used for non-logged-in "
"customers and :ref:`assign <sales/products/customer-pricelist-application>` "
"a regular pricelist (with actual prices) to customers with :ref:`portal "
"access <portal/access>`."
msgstr ""
"Pro skrytí cen veřejným návštěvníkům při zachování jejich viditelnosti pro "
"přihlášené zákazníky vytvořte ceník s nulovou cenou, který bude použit pro "
"nepřihlášené zákazníky, a :ref:`přiřaďte <sales/products/customer-pricelist-"
"application>` běžný ceník (se skutečnými cenami) zákazníkům s "
":ref:`přístupem na portál <portal/access>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products/prices.rst:333
msgid ":doc:`../customer_accounts`"
msgstr ":doc:`../customer_accounts`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo eCommerce allows you to configure various delivery methods, enabling "
"customers to choose their preferred option at :doc:`checkout <checkout>`. "
"These methods include :ref:`external providers <ecommerce/shipping/external-"
"provider>`, :ref:`custom options <ecommerce/shipping/custom-method>` such as "
"flat-rate or free shipping, local carriers via :doc:`Sendcloud </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping>` or :ref:`Based on Rules <inventory/"
"shipping/rules>`, and :ref:`in-store pickup <ecommerce/shipping/instore-"
"pickup>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Webbshop låter dig konfigurera olika leveransmetoder, vilket gör det "
"möjligt för kunder att välja sitt föredragna alternativ vid "
":doc:`utcheckning <checkout>`. Dessa metoder inkluderar :ref:`externa "
"leverantörer <ecommerce/shipping/external-provider>`, :ref:`anpassade "
"optioner <ecommerce/shipping/custom-method>` såsom fast pris eller fri "
"frakt, lokala transportföretag via :doc:`Sendcloud </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/"
"sendcloud_shipping>` eller :ref:`Baserat på regler <inventory/shipping/rules>"
"`, och :ref:`avhämtning i butik <ecommerce/shipping/instore-pickup>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:16
msgid "External provider integration"
msgstr "Integration med extern leverantör"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:18
msgid ""
"To handle product delivery, you can connect your database to :doc:`third-"
"party shipping carriers </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper>` "
"like :doc:`FedEx </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex>`, :doc:`UPS </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/"
"ups_credentials>`, or :doc:`DHL </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dhl_credentials>`. A shipping "
"connector links to these providers, automating :doc:`tracking labels </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/labels>` and shipping processes."
msgstr ""
"För att hantera produktleverans kan du ansluta din databas till "
":doc:`tredjepartsleverantörer </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper>` som :doc:`FedEx "
"</applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/fedex>`, :doc:`UPS </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/ups_credentials>` eller "
":doc:`DHL </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/dhl_credentials>`. En anslutning för transporter länkar "
"till dessa leverantörer och automatiserar :doc:`spårningsetiketter </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/labels>` och leveransprocesser."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:27
msgid ""
"To enable a third-party delivery provider, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, scroll to the :guilabel:`Delivery` section, "
"select the desired delivery provider(s), and :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"För att aktivera en tredjepartsleverantör, gå till "
":menuselection:`Hemsida --> Konfiguration --> Inställningar`, rulla till "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Leverans`, välj önskad(e) leverantör(er) och "
":guilabel:`Spara`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:31
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Delivery Methods` and "
"select the delivery method in the list to :ref:`configure it <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-delivery-method>`."
msgstr ""
"Gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> Konfiguration --> Leveransmetoder` och "
"välj leveransmetoden i listan för att :ref:`konfigurera den <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-delivery-method>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:35
msgid ""
":doc:`Third-party shipping carriers </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Tredjepartsleverantörer </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:37
msgid ":doc:`Gelato </applications/sales/sales/gelato>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Gelato </applications/sales/sales/gelato>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:40
msgid ""
"The field used to define additional fees **must** be filled **in your third-"
"party delivery provider account**, even if you do not plan to charge "
"customers any additional fee. If you do not want to apply a fee, enter `0`. "
"If the field is left empty, the delivery price cannot be calculated, and an "
"error message prompts the customer to select an alternative delivery method."
msgstr ""
"Fältet som används för att definiera ytterligare avgifter **måste** fyllas i "
"**på ditt konto hos tredjepartsleverantören**, även om du inte planerar att "
"debitera kunder några extra avgifter. Om du inte vill tillämpa en avgift, "
"ange `0`. Om fältet lämnas tomt kan leveranspriset inte beräknas, och ett "
"felmeddelande uppmanar kunden att välja en alternativ leveransmetod."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:46
msgid "Margin on delivery rate"
msgstr "Marginal på anrop"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:48
msgid ""
"To add an additional fee to the base shipping rate (e.g., to cover extra "
"costs), log into your carrier account and set the desired fee in the related "
"field. The shipping connector retrieves this fee and includes it in the "
"final price at checkout. Contact your carrier for further assistance with "
"this configuration."
msgstr ""
"För att lägga till en extra avgift till basanropet (t.ex. för att täcka "
"extra kostnader), logga in på ditt transportföretagskonto och ställ in "
"önskad avgift i relaterat fält. Anslutningen för transporter hämtar denna "
"avgift och inkluderar den i slutpriset vid utcheckning. Kontakta ditt "
"transportföretag för ytterligare hjälp med denna konfiguration."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:53
msgid ""
"Alternatively, enter `0` in your third-party shipping provider account, then "
"set the fee in Odoo. To do so, access the desired :ref:`shipping method's "
"form <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-delivery-method>` and enter the "
"fee in the :guilabel:`Margin on Rate` field to add a percentage to the "
"shipping costs and/or the :guilabel:`Additional margin` field to add a fixed "
"amount."
msgstr ""
"Alternativt anger du `0` i ditt konto hos tredjepartsleverantören och "
"ställer sedan in avgiften i Odoo. För att göra detta, öppna önskad "
":ref:`transportmetods formulär <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-"
"delivery-method>` och ange avgiften i fältet :guilabel:`Marginal på anrop` "
"för att lägga till en procentsats till transportkostnaderna och/eller i "
"fältet :guilabel:`Ytterligare marginal` för att lägga till ett fast belopp."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:60
msgid ""
"The field used to define additional fees cannot be left empty in your third-"
"party shipping provider account."
msgstr ""
"Fältet som används för att definiera ytterligare avgifter kan inte lämnas "
"tomt i ditt konto hos tredjepartsleverantören."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:66
msgid "Custom delivery method"
msgstr "Anpassad leveransmetod"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:68
msgid "Custom delivery methods must be created, for example:"
msgstr "Anpassade leveransmetoder måste skapas, till exempel:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:70
msgid ""
"to integrate delivery carriers through :doc:`Sendcloud </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/"
"sendcloud_shipping>`;"
msgstr ""
"för att integrera transportföretag genom :doc:`Sendcloud </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/"
"sendcloud_shipping>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:72
msgid ""
"to configure specific rules (e.g., to offer free shipping for orders above a "
"specific amount) for a specific provider;"
msgstr ""
"för att konfigurera specifika regler (t.ex. för att erbjuda fri frakt för "
"beställningar över ett visst belopp) för en specifik leverantör;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:74
msgid ""
"to configure :ref:`Fixed Price <inventory/shipping/fixed>` shipping, or "
"shipping :ref:`Based on Rules <inventory/shipping/rules>`."
msgstr ""
"för att konfigurera leverans till :ref:`fast pris <inventory/shipping/fixed>"
"`, eller leverans :ref:`baserat på regler <inventory/shipping/rules>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:77
msgid ""
"To create a custom delivery method, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Delivery Methods`, click :guilabel:`New`, and fill in "
"the :ref:`fields <inventory/shipping_receiving/shipping-methods-details>`."
msgstr ""
"För att skapa en anpassad leveransmetod, gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> "
"Konfiguration --> Leveransmetoder`, klicka på :guilabel:`Skapa` och fyll i "
":ref:`fälten <inventory/shipping_receiving/shipping-methods-details>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:81
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Provider` field, select :ref:`Based on Rules <inventory/"
"shipping/rules>` or :ref:`Fixed Price <inventory/shipping/fixed>`."
msgstr ""
"I fältet :guilabel:`Leverantör`, välj :ref:`Baserat på regler <inventory/"
"shipping/rules>` eller :ref:`Fast pris <inventory/shipping/fixed>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:85
msgid ""
"Upon :ref:`configuring <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-delivery-"
"method>` a delivery method, you can:"
msgstr ""
"Vid :ref:`konfigurering <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-delivery-"
"method>` av en leveransmetod kan du:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:88
msgid ""
"Restrict it :doc:`to a specific website <../website/configuration/"
"multi_website>` by selecting it in the :guilabel:`Website` field."
msgstr ""
"Begränsa den :doc:`till en specifik hemsida <../website/configuration/"
"multi_website>` genom att välja den i fältet :guilabel:`Hemsida`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:90
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Test Environment` smart button to switch to "
"the :guilabel:`Production Environment`. Then, click :guilabel:`Unpublished` "
"to :guilabel:`Publish` the delivery method and make it available to website "
"visitors."
msgstr ""
"Klicka på den smarta knappen :guilabel:`Testmiljö` för att växla till "
":guilabel:`Produktionsmiljö`. Klicka sedan på :guilabel:`Opublicerad` för "
"att :guilabel:`Publicera` leveransmetoden och göra den tillgänglig för "
"besökare på hemsidan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:93
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Availability` tab to define :ref:`conditions <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/availability>` for the delivery method based on the "
"order's content or destination."
msgstr ""
"Använd fliken :guilabel:`Tillgänglighet` för att definiera :ref:`villkor "
"<inventory/shipping_receiving/availability>` för leveransmetoden baserat på "
"beställningens innehåll eller destination."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:100
msgid "Click & Collect"
msgstr "Klicka och hämta"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:102
msgid ""
"To allow customers to reserve products online and pay for/collect them in-"
"store, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"För att låta kunder reservera produkter online och betala för/hämta dem i "
"butik, följ dessa steg:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:105
msgid ""
"Scroll to the :guilabel:`Delivery` section, enable :guilabel:`Click & "
"Collect`, and :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Rulla till sektionen :guilabel:`Leverans`, aktivera :guilabel:`Click & "
"Collect` och :guilabel:`Spara`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:107
msgid ""
"Click :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Configure Pickup Locations` "
"to :ref:`configure <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-delivery-method>` "
"the delivery method and ensure the :guilabel:`Provider` field is set "
"to :guilabel:`Pick up in store`."
msgstr ""
"Klicka på :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Konfigurera avhämtningsplatser` "
"för att :ref:`konfigurera <inventory/shipping_receiving/configure-delivery-"
"method>` leveransmetoden och se till att fältet :guilabel:`Leverantör` är "
"inställt på :guilabel:`Hämta i butik`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:110
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Stores` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a line` and select the "
"warehouse(s) where customers can collect their orders."
msgstr ""
"I fliken :guilabel:`Butiker`, klicka på :guilabel:`Lägg till en rad` och "
"välj det lager/de lager där kunder kan hämta sina beställningar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:112
msgid ""
"Once your setup is complete, click the :guilabel:`Unpublish` button to "
"change the status to :guilabel:`Publish` and make the delivery method "
"available to customers."
msgstr ""
"När din installation är klar klickar du på knappen :guilabel:`Avpublicera` "
"för att ändra status till :guilabel:`Publicera` och göra leveransmetoden "
"tillgänglig för kunder."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:116
msgid ""
"When the product is in stock, a location selector is displayed on "
"the :doc:`product <products>` and :doc:`checkout <checkout>` pages. "
"Customers cannot select a pickup location if the product is out of stock at "
"that location. The :ref:`Continue selling <ecommerce/products/stock-"
"management>` option for out-of-stock products is not supported."
msgstr ""
"När produkten finns i lager visas en platsväljare på :doc:`produkt <products>"
"`- och :doc:`kassa <checkout>`sidorna. Kunder kan inte välja en "
"avhämtningsplats om produkten är slut i lager på den platsen. Alternativet "
":ref:`Fortsätt sälja <ecommerce/products/stock-management>` för slutsålda "
"produkter stöds inte."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:120
msgid ""
"If the :ref:`Show Available Qty <ecommerce/products/stock-management>` "
"option is enabled for a product, customers can view the stock quantity "
"available for each warehouse in the location selector on the product page."
msgstr ""
"Om alternativet :ref:`Visa tillgängligt antal <ecommerce/products/stock-"
"management>` är aktiverat för en produkt kan kunder se det tillgängliga "
"lagerantalet för varje lager i platsväljaren på produktsidan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:123
msgid ""
"Each warehouse must have a **complete address** to ensure its location is "
"accurately displayed to customers. Incomplete addresses prevent the "
"warehouse from being shown."
msgstr ""
"Varje lager måste ha en **fullständig adress** för att säkerställa att dess "
"plats visas korrekt för kunderna. Ofullständiga adresser förhindrar att "
"lagret visas."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:125
msgid ""
"In a multi-company environment, the company assigned to the warehouse must "
"match the company assigned to the website on which the delivery method is "
"used. If the companies differ, the pickup location cannot be selected."
msgstr ""
"I en multi-företagsmiljö måste företaget som tilldelats lagret matcha "
"företaget som tilldelats hemsidan på vilken leveransmetoden används. Om "
"företagen skiljer sig åt kan avhämtningsplatsen inte väljas."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:128
msgid "The Click & Collect option is not available for services."
msgstr "Click & Collect-alternativet är inte tillgängligt för tjänster."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:3
msgid "eLearning"
msgstr "eLärande"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:5
msgid ""
"The **eLearning** app allows you to easily upload content, define learning "
"objectives, manage attendees, assess students' progress, and even set up "
"rewards. Engaging participants in a meaningful learning experience enhances "
"their attentiveness and fosters heightened productivity."
msgstr ""
"Med appen **eLearning** kan du enkelt ladda upp innehåll, definiera "
"inlärningsmål, hantera deltagare, bedöma elevernas framsteg och till och med "
"skapa belöningar. Att engagera deltagarna i en meningsfull "
"inlärningsupplevelse ökar deras uppmärksamhet och främjar ökad produktivitet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:10
msgid ""
"You can manage your eLearning content on the **front end** or the **back "
"end**. The **front end** allows you to create content quickly from your "
"website, while the **back end** provides additional options and allows "
"collaboration. This documentation focuses on using the back end to create "
"your content."
msgstr ""
"Du kan hantera ditt eLearning-innehåll på **front end** eller **back end**. "
"Med **front end** kan du snabbt skapa innehåll från din webbplats, medan "
"**back end** ger ytterligare alternativ och möjliggör samarbete. Denna "
"dokumentation fokuserar på att använda backend för att skapa ditt innehåll."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:16
msgid "`Odoo Tutorials: eLearning <https://www.odoo.com/slides/elearning-56>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: eLearning <https://www.odoo.com/slides/elearning-56>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:21
msgid "Courses"
msgstr "Löpningar"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:23
msgid ""
"To get an overview of all courses, go to :menuselection:`eLearning --> "
"Courses --> Courses`."
msgstr ""
"För att få en översikt över alla kurser, gå till "
":menuselection:`eLearning --> Kurser --> Kurser`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:25
msgid ""
"Click on a course card to edit the course on the back end. "
"Click :guilabel:`View course` to access the course on the front end."
msgstr ""
"Klicka på ett kurskort för att redigera kursen i backend. Klicka på "
":guilabel:`Visa kurs` för att komma åt kursen i frontend."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:31
msgid "Course creation"
msgstr "Skapande av kurs"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:33
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`New` to create a new course. In the form that opens, add "
"a :guilabel:`Course Title` and one or more :guilabel:`Tags` to categorize "
"the course and :ref:`allow users to filter courses based on their tags "
"<elearning/course-groups>`. To add an image to illustrate the course, hover "
"your mouse on the camera placeholder image and click on :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` :guilabel:`(Edit)`."
msgstr ""
"Klicka på :guilabel:`Ny` för att skapa en ny kurs. I formuläret som öppnas, "
"lägg till en :guilabel:`Kursrubrik` och en eller flera :guilabel:`Taggar` "
"för att kategorisera kursen och :ref:`tillåta användare att filtrera kurser "
"baserat på deras taggar <elearning/course-groups>`. För att lägga till en "
"bild som illustrerar kursen, håll musen över kameraplatsens platshållarbild "
"och klicka på :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(Redigera)`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:39
msgid ""
"Four tabs allow you to edit your course further: :ref:`Content <elearning/"
"content>`, :ref:`Description <elearning/description>`, :ref:`Options "
"<elearning/options>`, and :ref:`Karma <elearning/karma>`."
msgstr ""
"Fyra flikar låter dig redigera din kurs ytterligare: :ref:`Innehåll "
"<elearning/content>`, :ref:`Beskrivning <elearning/description>`, "
":ref:`Optioner <elearning/options>` och :ref:`Karma <elearning/karma>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:None
msgid "Create your elearning course."
msgstr "Skapa din elearningkurs."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:49
msgid "Content tab"
msgstr "Fliken Innehåll"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:51
msgid ""
"This tab allows you to manage the course content. Click :guilabel:`Add "
"Section` to divide the course into different sections. Click :guilabel:`Add "
"Content` to create :ref:`content items <elearning/content-creation>`. "
"Click :guilabel:`Add Certification` to assess the attendees' level of "
"understanding, certify their skills, and motivate them. **Certification** is "
"part of the :doc:`Surveys <../marketing/surveys/create>` app."
msgstr ""
"Denna flik låter dig hantera kursinnehållet. Klicka på :guilabel:`Lägg till "
"sektion` för att dela upp kursen i olika sektioner. Klicka på "
":guilabel:`Lägg till innehåll` för att skapa :ref:`innehållsobjekt "
"<elearning/content-creation>`. Klicka på :guilabel:`Lägg till certifiering` "
"för att bedöma deltagarnas förståelsenivå, certifiera deras färdigheter och "
"motivera dem. **Certifiering** är en del av appen :doc:`Enkäter <../"
"marketing/surveys/create>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:60
#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:266
msgid "Description tab"
msgstr "Fliken Beskrivning"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:62
msgid ""
"You can add a short description or information related to the course in "
"the :guilabel:`Description` tab. It appears under the course title on your "
"website."
msgstr ""
"Du kan lägga till en kort beskrivning eller information relaterad till "
"kursen i fliken :guilabel:`Beskrivning`. Den visas under kursrubriken på din "
"hemsida."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:None
msgid "Add a description to your course."
msgstr "Lägg till en beskrivning av din kurs."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:71
#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:91
msgid "Options tab"
msgstr "Fliken Alternativ"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:73
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Options` tab, different configurations are "
"available: :ref:`Course <elearning/options-course>`, :ref:`Communication "
"<elearning/options-communication>`, :ref:`Access rights <elearning/options-"
"access-rights>`, and :ref:`Display <elearning/options-display>`."
msgstr ""
"I fliken :guilabel:`Optioner` finns olika konfigurationer tillgängliga: "
":ref:`Kurs <elearning/options-course>`, :ref:`Betalningsreferens <elearning/"
"options-communication>`, :ref:`Åtkomstbehörighet <elearning/options-access-"
"rights>` och :ref:`Skärm <elearning/options-display>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:None
msgid "Overview of the Options tab"
msgstr "Översikt över fliken Alternativ"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:84
msgid "Course"
msgstr "Kurs"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:86
msgid ""
"Assign a :guilabel:`Responsible` user for the course. If you have multiple "
"websites, use the :guilabel:`Website` field to display the course only on "
"the selected website."
msgstr ""
"Tilldela en :guilabel:`Ansvarig` användare för kursen. Om du har flera "
"hemsidor, använd fältet :guilabel:`Hemsida` för att visa kursen endast på "
"den valda hemsidan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:92
msgid "Communication"
msgstr "Kommunikation"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:94
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allow Reviews`: Enable this option to allow attendees to like, "
"comment on, and submit reviews for the course content."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tillåt recensioner`: Aktivera detta alternativ för att tillåta "
"deltagare att gilla, kommentera och skicka in recensioner för kursinnehållet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:96
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Forum`: Add a dedicated forum to the course (only shown if "
"the :guilabel:`Forum` feature is enabled in the :ref:`eLearning settings "
"<elearning/settings>`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forum`: Lägg till ett dedikerat forum till kursen (visas endast "
"om funktionen :guilabel:`Forum` är aktiverad i :ref:`eLearning-"
"inställningarna <elearning/settings>`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:98
msgid ""
":guilabel:`New Content Notification`: Select an email template to send "
"emails to attendees when you upload new content items. Click on :icon:`oi-"
"arrow-right` :guilabel:`Internal link` to access the email template editor."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Meddelande om nytt innehåll`: Välj en e-postmall för att skicka e-"
"post till deltagare när du laddar upp nya innehållsobjekt. Klicka på "
":icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Intern länk` för att få åtkomst till "
"redigeraren för e-postmallar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:101
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Completion Notification`: Select an email template to send emails "
"to attendees once they reach the end of the course. Click on :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Internal link` to access the email template editor."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Slutförandemeddelande`: Välj en e-postmall för att skicka e-post "
"till deltagare när de når slutet av kursen. Klicka på :icon:`oi-arrow-right` "
":guilabel:`Intern länk` för att få åtkomst till redigeraren för e-postmallar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:106
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Mailing` feature is enabled in the :ref:`eLearning "
"settings <elearning/settings>`, a :guilabel:`Contact Attendees` button at "
"the top left of the course form allows you to send mass mailings to people "
"enrolled in the course."
msgstr ""
"Om funktionen :guilabel:`Utskick` är aktiverad i :ref:`eLearning-"
"inställningarna <elearning/settings>`, finns en knapp :guilabel:`Kontakta "
"deltagare` längst upp till vänster i kursformuläret som gör att du kan "
"skicka massutskick till personer som är registrerade i kursen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:113
msgid "Access rights"
msgstr "Tillträdesrättigheter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:115
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Prerequisites`: Set one or more other courses that users are "
"advised to complete before accessing the course."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Krav`: Ange en eller flera andra kurser som användare "
"rekommenderas att slutföra innan de får tillgång till kursen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:117
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Prerequisite Of`: If the course has been defined as a "
"prerequisite for one or more courses, this read-only field displays the "
"course name(s)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Krav för`: Om kursen har definierats som ett krav för en eller "
"flera kurser, visar detta skrivskyddade fält kursnamnet/kursnamnen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:119
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Show course to`: Define who can access the course and its "
"content. Select :guilabel:`Everyone`, :guilabel:`Signed In`, "
"or :guilabel:`Course Attendees`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Visa kurs för`: Definiera vem som kan komma åt kursen och dess "
"innehåll. Välj :guilabel:`Alla`, :guilabel:`Inloggad` eller "
":guilabel:`Kursdeltagare`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:121
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Enroll Policy`: Define how people enroll in the course. Select:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Registreringspolicy`: Definiera hur personer registrerar sig till "
"kursen. Välj:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:123
msgid ":guilabel:`Open`: to make the course available to anyone."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Öppen`: för att göra kursen tillgänglig för alla."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:124
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On Invitation`: to restrict enrollment to invited attendees only. "
"If enabled, provide an :guilabel:`Enroll Message` explaining the enrollment "
"process. This message is displayed on your website beneath the course title. "
"To send invite to attendees, click :guilabel:`Invite` and "
"either:guilabel:`Copy` the link or toggle :guilabel:`Send by Email` to send "
"the invitation via email."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`På inbjudan`: för att begränsa registrering till endast inbjudna "
"deltagare. Om aktiverad, ange ett :guilabel:`Registreringsmeddelande` som "
"förklarar registreringsprocessen. Detta meddelande visas på din hemsida "
"under kurstiteln. För att skicka inbjudan till deltagare, klicka på "
":guilabel:`Bjud in` och antingen:guilabel:`Kopiera` länken eller aktivera "
":guilabel:`Skicka via e-post` för att skicka inbjudan via e-post."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:129
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On Payment`: to restrict enrollment to users who purchase the "
"course. If enabled, select the :guilabel:`Product` to be used. This option "
"requires the :guilabel:`Paid Courses` feature to be enabled in "
"the :ref:`eLearning settings <elearning/settings>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vid betalning`: för att begränsa registrering till användare som "
"köper kursen. Om aktiverad, välj :guilabel:`Produkt` som ska användas. Detta "
"alternativ kräver att funktionen :guilabel:`Betalda kurser` är aktiverad i "
":ref:`eLearning-inställningarna <elearning/settings>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:134
msgid ""
"Only products set up with :guilabel:`Course` as their :guilabel:`Product "
"Type` are available for selection."
msgstr ""
"Endast produkter som konfigurerats med :guilabel:`Kurs` som sin "
":guilabel:`Produkttyp` är tillgängliga för val."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:140
msgid "Display"
msgstr "Display"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:142
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Training`: The course content appears as a training program, and "
"the courses must be taken in the proposed order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Utbildning`: Kursinnehållet visas som ett utbildningsprogram och "
"kurserna måste tas i den föreslagna ordningen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:144
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Documentation`: The content is available in any order. Use "
"the :guilabel:`Featured Content` field to define which content items are "
"promoted on the course homepage."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dokumentation`: Innehållet är tillgängligt i valfri ordning. "
"Använd fältet :guilabel:`Utvalt innehåll` för att definiera vilka "
"innehållsobjekt som framhävs på kursens startsida."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:150
msgid "Karma tab"
msgstr "Karma-fliken"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:152
msgid "This tab is about gamification to make eLearning fun and interactive."
msgstr ""
"Denna flik handlar om spelifiering för att göra eLearning roligt och "
"interaktivt."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:154
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Rewards` section, choose how many karma points you want to "
"grant attendees when they :guilabel:`Review` or :guilabel:`Finish` a course."
msgstr ""
"I avsnittet :guilabel:`Belöningar`, välj hur många karmapoäng du vill ge "
"deltagare när de :guilabel:`Recenserar` eller :guilabel:`Slutför` en kurs."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:157
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Access Rights` section, define the karma points needed "
"to :guilabel:`Add Review`, :guilabel:`Add Comment`, or :guilabel:`Vote` on "
"the course."
msgstr ""
"I avsnittet :guilabel:`Åtkomstbehörighet`, definiera de karmapoäng som krävs "
"för att :guilabel:`Lägga till recension`, :guilabel:`Lägga till kommentar`, "
"eller :guilabel:`Rösta` på kursen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:163
msgid "Course groups"
msgstr "Kursgrupper"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:165
msgid ""
"**Course Groups** allow users to filter the :guilabel:`All Courses` "
"dashboard on your website and find the course that meets their interests, "
"needs, level, etc."
msgstr ""
"**Kursgrupper** gör det möjligt för användare att filtrera :guilabel:`Alla "
"kurser`-dashboarden på din hemsida och hitta kursen som uppfyller deras "
"intressen, behov, nivå osv."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:168
msgid ""
"To manage them, go to :menuselection:`eLearning --> Configuration --> Course "
"Groups`. Click :guilabel:`New` to create a new course group. Add "
"the :guilabel:`Course Group Name`, enable :guilabel:`Menu Entry` to allow "
"users to search by course group on the website, and add tags in "
"the :guilabel:`Tag Name` column. For each tag, you can select a "
"corresponding color."
msgstr ""
"För att hantera dem, gå till :menuselection:`eLearning --> Konfiguration --> "
"Kursgrupper`. Klicka på :guilabel:`Skapa` för att skapa en ny kursgrupp. "
"Lägg till :guilabel:`Kursgruppsnamn`, aktivera :guilabel:`Menyval` för att "
"tillåta användare att söka efter kursgrupp på hemsidan, och lägg till taggar "
"i kolumnen :guilabel:`Taggnamn`. För varje tagg kan du välja en motsvarande "
"färg."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:176
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "Inställningar"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:178
msgid ""
"The following options are available in the eLearning settings. Go "
"to :menuselection:`eLearning --> Configuration --> Settings`, then enable "
"the desired feature:"
msgstr ""
"Följande alternativ är tillgängliga i eLearning-inställningarna. Gå till "
":menuselection:`eLearning --> Konfiguration --> Inställningar`, aktivera "
"sedan önskad funktion:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:181
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Certifications`: Assess attendees' knowledge and provide official "
"certification of their skills."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Certifieringar`: Bedöm deltagarnas kunskap och tillhandahåll "
"officiell certifiering av deras färdigheter."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:183
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Paid Courses`: Sell course access directly through your website "
"and track revenue."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Betalda kurser`: Sälj kursåtkomst direkt via din hemsida och "
"spåra intäkter."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:184
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Mailing`: Send mass mailings to keep all attendees informed and "
"up to date."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Utskick`: Skicka massutskick för att hålla alla deltagare "
"informerade och uppdaterade."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:185
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Forum`: Build a community space where attendees can ask questions "
"and help each other."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forum`: Bygg ett gemenskapsutrymme där deltagare kan ställa "
"frågor och hjälpa varandra."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:190
msgid "Content"
msgstr "Innehåll"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:192
msgid ""
"To manage course content, go to :menuselection:`eLearning --> Courses --> "
"Contents`. Click :guilabel:`New` to create a content item. Add "
"the :guilabel:`Content Title` and any desired :ref:`Tags <elearning/content-"
"tags>`, then fill in the required information in the different tabs."
msgstr ""
"För att hantera kursinnehåll, gå till :menuselection:`eLearning --> "
"Kurser --> Innehåll`. Klicka på :guilabel:`Skapa` för att skapa ett "
"innehållsobjekt. Lägg till :guilabel:`Innehållsrubrik` och eventuella "
"önskade :ref:`Taggar <elearning/content-tags>`, fyll sedan i nödvändig "
"information i de olika flikarna."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:None
msgid "Create your content."
msgstr "Skapa ditt innehåll."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:200
msgid ""
"You can also create new content from within a course. Go "
"to :menuselection:`eLearning --> Courses --> Courses`, click the relevant "
"course card, then click :guilabel:`Add content` at the bottom of "
"the :guilabel:`Content` tab."
msgstr ""
"Du kan också skapa nytt innehåll inifrån en kurs. Gå till "
":menuselection:`eLearning --> Kurser --> Kurser`, klicka på relevant "
"kurskort, klicka sedan på :guilabel:`Lägg till innehåll` längst ned i fliken "
":guilabel:`Innehåll`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:207
msgid "Document tab"
msgstr "Fliken Dokument"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:209
msgid "For each content type, provide the following information:"
msgstr "För varje Typ av Innehåll, ange följande information:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:211
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Course`: Select the course to which the content item belongs."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Kurs`: Välj kursen som innehållsobjektet tillhör."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:212
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Content Type`: Select the relevant :ref:`content type <elearning/"
"content-type>` and provide the required information."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Typ av Innehåll`: Välj relevant :ref:`typ av innehåll <elearning/"
"content-type>` och ange nödvändig information."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:214
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Responsible`: Select the user responsible for the content item. "
"By default, this is the user who creates the course, but another user can be "
"selected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ansvarig`: Välj den användare som är ansvarig för "
"innehållsobjektet. Som standard är detta den användare som skapar kursen, "
"men en annan användare kan väljas."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:216
msgid ":guilabel:`Duration`: Enter the time required to complete the lesson."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Giltighetstid`: Ange den tid som krävs för att slutföra lektionen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:217
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allow Preview`: Enable this if the content should be accessible "
"to anyone."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tillåt Förhandsvisa`: Aktivera detta om innehållet ska vara "
"tillgängligt för alla."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:220
msgid ""
"If the :ref:`Content Type <elearning/content-type>` is :guilabel:`Document`, "
"enabling :guilabel:`Allow Download` allows users to download the content."
msgstr ""
"Om :ref:`Typ av Innehåll <elearning/content-type>` är :guilabel:`Dokument`, "
"tillåter aktivering av :guilabel:`Tillåt Nedladdning` användare att ladda "
"ner innehållet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:223
msgid ""
"Two read-only fields provide data about how often the content item is viewed:"
msgstr "Två skrivskyddade fält ger data om hur ofta innehållsobjektet visas:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:225
msgid ""
":guilabel:`# of Public Views`: displays the number of views from non-"
"enrolled participants."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`# Offentliga Visningar`: visar antalet visningar från icke-"
"registrerade deltagare."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:226
msgid ""
":guilabel:`# Total Views`: displays the total number of views (non-enrolled "
"and enrolled participants)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`# Totalt antal visningar`: visar det totala antalet visningar "
"(icke inskrivna och inskrivna deltagare)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:None
msgid "Provide information about the content."
msgstr "Ange information om innehållet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:235
msgid "Content types"
msgstr "Typer av innehåll"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:237
msgid "You can add the following content types:"
msgstr "Du kan lägga till följande typer av innehåll:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:239
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Image`: To upload an image, select :guilabel:`Upload from "
"Device`, click :guilabel:`Upload your file`, then select the relevant file. "
"Supported formats include JPG, JPEG, PNG, SVG, GIF, and WEBP. The maximum "
"file size is 25MB."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bild`: För att ladda upp en bild, välj :guilabel:`Ladda upp från "
"Enhet`, klicka på :guilabel:`Ladda upp din fil` och välj sedan relevant fil. "
"Format som stöds inkluderar JPG, JPEG, PNG, SVG, GIF och WEBP. Den maximala "
"filstorleken är 25MB."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:243
msgid ""
"Alternatively, to add an image saved on Google Drive, "
"select :guilabel:`Retrieve from Google Drive`, then add the Google Drive "
"link to the image."
msgstr ""
"Alternativt, för att lägga till en bild som är sparad på Google Drive, välj "
":guilabel:`Hämta från Google Drive` och lägg sedan till Google Drive-länken "
"till bilden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:246
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Article`: Articles are website pages that are customized using "
"the website builder on your website's front end."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Artikel`: Artiklar är hemsidor som anpassas med hjälp av "
"hemsidesverktyget på din hemsidas frontend."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:249
msgid ""
"With the :guilabel:`Course` selected, click the :guilabel:`Go to Website` "
"smart button, then, at the top-right of the screen, click :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` :guilabel:`(Edit)`. Write the article's content and :doc:`customize "
"the page using the website builder </applications/websites/website/"
"web_design>`."
msgstr ""
"Med :guilabel:`Kurs` vald, klicka på den smarta knappen :guilabel:`Gå till "
"Hemsida`, klicka sedan längst upp till höger på skärmen på :icon:`fa-pencil` "
":guilabel:`(Redigera)`. Skriv artikelns innehåll och :doc:`anpassa sidan med "
"hjälp av hemsidesverktyget </applications/websites/website/web_design>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:253
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Document`: To upload a document, select :guilabel:`Upload from "
"Device`, click :guilabel:`Upload your file`, then select the relevant file. "
"Only PDF documents can be uploaded."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dokument`: För att ladda upp ett dokument, välj :guilabel:`Ladda "
"upp från Enhet`, klicka på :guilabel:`Ladda upp din fil` och välj sedan "
"relevant fil. Endast PDF-dokument kan laddas upp."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:256
msgid ""
"Alternatively, to add a Google Slides presentation, Google Doc document, or "
"Google Sheets spreadsheet, click :guilabel:`Retrieve from Google Drive` and "
"add the Google Drive link to the file."
msgstr ""
"Alternativt, för att lägga till en Google Slides-presentation, ett Google "
"Docs-dokument eller ett Google Sheets-kalkylark, klicka på :guilabel:`Hämta "
"från Google Drive` och lägg till Google Drive-länken till filen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:260
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Video`: Add the YouTube, Google Drive, or Vimeo link to the video."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Video`: Lägg till YouTube-, Google Drive- eller Vimeo-länken till "
"videon."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:261
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Quiz`: Open the :ref:`Quiz tab <elearning/content-quiz>` to "
"create a quiz."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Quiz`: Öppna :ref:`Quiz-fliken <elearning/content-quiz>` för att "
"skapa ett quiz."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:268
msgid ""
"Add a description for the content. This text is displayed in "
"the :guilabel:`About` section of the content item on your website."
msgstr ""
"Lägg till en beskrivning för innehållet. Denna text visas i :guilabel:`Om`-"
"sektionen av innehållsobjektet på din hemsida."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:274
msgid "Additional Resources tab"
msgstr "Fliken Ytterligare resurser"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:276
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` to add a link or a file that supports your "
"participants' learning. The resource appears in the course content on your "
"website."
msgstr ""
"Klicka :guilabel:`Lägg till en rad` för att lägga till en länk eller en fil "
"som stöder dina deltagares lärande. Resursen visas i kursinnehållet på din "
"hemsida."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:None
msgid "Additional ressources"
msgstr "Ytterligare resurser"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:285
msgid "Quiz tab"
msgstr "Fliken Quiz"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:287
msgid ""
"From this tab, you can create a quiz to assess your students at the end of "
"the course."
msgstr ""
"Från denna flik kan du skapa ett quiz för att bedöma dina elever i slutet av "
"kursen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:289
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Points Rewards` section allows you to assign karma points "
"based on how many attempts are needed to answer correctly. To create a "
"question, click :guilabel:`Add a line`, enter the :guilabel:`Question Name`, "
"and add possible answers. Mark the correct answer(s) by "
"selecting :guilabel:`Is correct answer`. You can also use "
"the :guilabel:`Comment` field to provide additional information when an "
"answer is selected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Poängbelöningar`-sektionen låter dig tilldela karmapoäng baserat "
"på hur många försök som behövs för att svara rätt. För att skapa en fråga, "
"klicka :guilabel:`Lägg till en rad`, ange :guilabel:`Frågans namn`, och lägg "
"till möjliga svar. Markera det rätta svaret/de rätta svaren genom att välja "
":guilabel:`Är korrekt svar`. Du kan också använda :guilabel:`Kommentar`-"
"fältet för att ge ytterligare information när ett svar väljs."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:298
msgid "Content Tags"
msgstr "Etiketter för innehåll"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:300
msgid ""
"**Content Tags** are visible on the :guilabel:`Contents` dashboard of a "
"course on your website, and can help users identify the kind of content a "
"particular lesson contains, e.g., theory, or exercises."
msgstr ""
"**Innehållstaggar** är synliga på :guilabel:`Innehåll`-dashboarden för en "
"kurs på din hemsida, och kan hjälpa användare att identifiera vilken typ av "
"innehåll en viss lektion innehåller, t.ex. teori eller övningar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:303
msgid ""
"To manage content tags, go to :menuselection:`eLearning --> Configuration --"
"> Content Tags`. Click :guilabel:`New` to create a new tag."
msgstr ""
"För att hantera innehållstaggar, gå till :menuselection:`eLearning --> "
"Konfiguration --> Innehållstaggar`. Klicka :guilabel:`Ny` för att skapa en "
"ny tagg."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:309
msgid "Publish courses and content"
msgstr "Publicera kurser och innehåll"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:311
msgid ""
"Courses and content items must be published from the front end to be "
"available to your audience. To access the front end, click the :guilabel:`Go "
"to Website` smart button at the top of the course form or an individual "
"content form."
msgstr ""
"Kurser och innehållsobjekt måste publiceras från framsidan för att vara "
"tillgängliga för din målgrupp. För att komma åt framsidan, klicka på den "
"smarta knappen :guilabel:`Gå till hemsida` längst upp i kursformuläret eller "
"ett individuellt innehållsformulär."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:315
msgid "A course and its content items are published separately:"
msgstr "En kurs och dess innehållsobjekt publiceras separat:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:317
msgid ""
"To publish a course, access the main course page, then toggle the switch in "
"the upper-right corner from :guilabel:`Unpublished` to :guilabel:`Published`."
msgstr ""
"För att publicera en kurs, gå till huvudkurssidan och växla sedan "
"omkopplaren i övre högra hörnet från :guilabel:`Avpublicerad` till "
":guilabel:`Publicerad`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:319
msgid ""
"To publish individual content items, click on an item to open it, then "
"toggle the switch from :guilabel:`Unpublished` to :guilabel:`Published`."
msgstr ""
"För att publicera individuella innehållsobjekt, klicka på ett objekt för att "
"öppna det och växla sedan omkopplaren från :guilabel:`Avpublicerad` till "
":guilabel:`Publicerad`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:None
msgid "Publish your content."
msgstr "Publicera ditt innehåll."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:326
msgid ""
"When publishing a new course, publish the individual content items before "
"publishing the course itself. Published content is only available to your "
"audience once the course it is part of is published."
msgstr ""
"När du publicerar en ny kurs, publicera de individuella innehållsobjekten "
"innan du publicerar själva kursen. Publicerat innehåll är endast "
"tillgängligt för din målgrupp när kursen den är en del av är publicerad."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:330
msgid ""
"To unpublish a course or an individual content item, open the course or "
"item, then toggle the switch from :guilabel:`Published` "
"to :guilabel:`Unpublished`."
msgstr ""
"För att avpublicera en kurs eller ett individuellt innehållsobjekt, öppna "
"kursen eller objektet och växla sedan omkopplaren från "
":guilabel:`Publicerad` till :guilabel:`Avpublicerad`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/elearning.rst:334
msgid ""
"Unpublishing a course renders the course *and* its content unavailable to "
"your audience."
msgstr ""
"Att avpublicera en kurs gör kursen *och* dess innehåll otillgängligt för din "
"målgrupp."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:3
msgid "Forum"
msgstr "Forum"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:5
msgid ""
"**Odoo Forum** is a question-and-answer forum designed with providing "
"customer support in mind. Adding a forum to a website enables you to build a "
"community, encourage engagement, and share knowledge."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo Forum** är ett fråge- och svarsforum som är utformat med tanke på "
"kundsupport. Genom att lägga till ett forum på en webbplats kan du bygga upp "
"en gemenskap, uppmuntra engagemang och dela med dig av kunskap."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:12
msgid "Create a forum"
msgstr "Skapa ett forum"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:14
msgid ""
"To create or edit a forum, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --"
"> Forum: Forums`. Click :guilabel:`New` or select an existing forum and "
"configure the following elements."
msgstr ""
"För att skapa eller redigera ett forum, gå till :menuselection:`Webbplats --"
"> Konfiguration --> Forum: Forum`. Klicka på :guilabel:`New` eller välj ett "
"befintligt forum och konfigurera följande element."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:17
msgid ":guilabel:`Forum Name`: add the name of the forum."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Forumnamn`: lägg till namnet på forumet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:19
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Mode`: select :guilabel:`Questions` to enable marking an answer "
"as best, meaning questions then appear as *solved*, "
"or :guilabel:`Discussions` if the feature is not needed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Mode`: välj :guilabel:`Questions` för att markera ett svar som "
"bäst, vilket innebär att frågor då visas som *solved*, "
"eller :guilabel:`Discussions` om funktionen inte behövs."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:23
msgid ""
"Regardless of the selected mode, only **one answer** per user is allowed on "
"a single post. Commenting multiple times is allowed, however."
msgstr ""
"Oavsett vilket läge som valts tillåts endast **ett svar** per användare på "
"ett och samma inlägg. Det är dock tillåtet att kommentera flera gånger."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:26
msgid ":guilabel:`Default Sort`: choose how questions are sorted by default."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Default Sort`: välj hur frågorna ska sorteras som standard."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:28
msgid ":guilabel:`Newest`: by latest question posting date"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Newest`: efter senaste inläggsdatum för frågan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:29
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Last Updated`: by latest posting activity date (answers and "
"comments included)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Last Updated`: efter datum för senaste inläggsaktivitet (svar och "
"kommentarer inkluderade)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:30
msgid ":guilabel:`Most Voted`: by highest vote tally"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Most Voted`: efter högsta röstetal"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:31
msgid ":guilabel:`Relevance`: by post relevancy (determined by a formula)"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Relevans`: efter inläggets relevans (bestäms av en formel)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:32
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Answered`: by likelihood to be answered (determined by a formula)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Answered`: med sannolikhet att bli besvarad (bestäms av en formel)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:35
msgid ""
"Users have several sorting options (total replies, total views, last "
"activity) on the forum front end."
msgstr ""
"Användarna har flera sorteringsalternativ (totalt antal svar, totalt antal "
"visningar, senaste aktivitet) på forumets frontend."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:38
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Privacy`: select :guilabel:`Public` to let anyone view the "
"forum, :guilabel:`Signed In` to make it visible only for signed-in users, "
"or :guilabel:`Some users` to make it visible only for a specific user access "
"group by selecting one :guilabel:`Authorized Group`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Privacy`: välj :guilabel:`Public` för att låta alla se "
"forumet, :guilabel:`Signed In` för att göra det synligt endast för inloggade "
"användare, eller :guilabel:`Some users` för att göra det synligt endast för "
"en viss användargrupp genom att välja en :guilabel:`Authorized Group`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:42
msgid ""
"Next, configure the :ref:`karma gains <forum/karma-gains>` and "
"the :ref:`karma-related rights <forum/karma-related-rights>`."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurera sedan :ref:`karma gains <forum/karma-gains>` och :ref:`karma-"
"related rights <forum/karma-related-rights>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:48
msgid "Karma points"
msgstr "Karma poäng"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:50
msgid ""
"Karma points can be given to users based on different forum interactions. "
"They can be used to determine which forum functionalities users can access, "
"from being able to vote on posts to having moderator rights. They are also "
"used to set user :ref:`ranks <forum/ranks>`."
msgstr ""
"Karma-poäng kan ges till användare baserat på olika foruminteraktioner. De "
"kan användas för att bestämma vilka forumfunktioner användare kan få "
"tillgång till, från att kunna rösta på inlägg till att ha "
"moderatorrättigheter. De används också för att ställa in "
"användarens :ref:`ranks <forum/ranks>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:55
msgid ""
"A user's karma points are shared across all forums, courses, etc., of a "
"single Odoo website."
msgstr ""
"En användares karmapoäng delas över alla forum, kurser etc. på en enda Odoo-"
"webbplats."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:56
msgid ""
"eLearning users can earn karma points through different :ref:`course "
"interactions <elearning/karma>` and by :ref:`completing quizzes <elearning/"
"content-quiz>`."
msgstr ""
"eLearning-användare kan tjäna karmapoäng genom olika :ref:`kursinteraktioner "
"<elearning/karma>` och genom att :ref:`slutföra quiz <elearning/content-quiz>"
"`."

