"Change posted questions' :ref:`tags <forum/tags>` (if you have the right to "
"edit them)."
msgstr ""
"Ändra postade frågors :ref:`tags <forum/tags>` (om du har rätt att redigera "
"dem)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:203
