"Scroll down to the :guilabel:`Shop - Products` section and select "
"the :guilabel:`Pricelists` option :guilabel:`Multiple prices per product`."
msgstr ""
"Scrolla ner till sektionen :guilabel:`Shop - Products` och välj "
