msgstr "Přidejte :guilabel:`Widget name`, abyste jej snadno identifikovali."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:37
msgid ""
"Click :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`Add Hostnames`, enter a custom hostname "
"(e.g., *example.com* or *subdomain.example.com*), then click :guilabel:`Add` "
"twice."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`Add Hostnames`, zadejte vlastní název "
"hostitele (např. *example.com* nebo *subdomain.example.com*), poté klikněte "
"dvakrát na :guilabel:`Add`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:39
msgid "Select a :guilabel:`Widget Mode`:"
msgstr "Välj en :guilabel:`Widget Mode`:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:41
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Managed` mode is **recommended**, as it allows Turnstile to "
"prompt visitors to confirm they are human when necessary."
msgstr ""
"Režim :guilabel:`Managed` je **doporučený**, protože umožňuje službě "
"Turnstile vyzvat návštěvníky, aby v případě potřeby potvrdili, že jsou lidé."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:0
msgid "Cloudflare Turnstile human verification widget"
msgstr "Cloudflare Turnstile widget för mänsklig verifiering"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:47
msgid ""
"For the :guilabel:`Non-interactive` and :guilabel:`Invisible` modes, "
"visitors are never prompted to interact. In :guilabel:`Non-interactive` "
"mode, a loading widget can be displayed to warn visitors that Turnstile "
"protects the form; however, the widget is not supported by Odoo."
msgstr ""
"I lägena :guilabel:`Non-interactive` och :guilabel:`Invisible` uppmanas "
"besökarna aldrig att interagera. I läget :guilabel:`Non-interactive` kan en "
"laddningswidget visas för att varna besökare om att Turnstile skyddar "
"formuläret; widgeten stöds dock inte av Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:52
msgid ""
"If the Turnstile check fails, visitors are not able to submit the form, and "
